\mt1 Yacuwa  
\c 1
\s1 Ňėumur n SIDI i uŠĻ≠effu n temmurt n Ken…õan  
\m
\v 1 Awarni i Ňômewt n Musa, amsexxar n SIDI, issiweŇô SIDI ak-d Yacuwa, mmis n Nun, amsexxar n Musa, inna: \x ‚óė \xo 1:1 \xt A…õwd. 34:5;1:38\x*  
\v 2 ‚ÄúMusa, amsexxar inu immut. Ňėexxu kkar, ekk x L‚ÄôUrdun-a, cek d marra Ňôgens-a, …£ar temmurt i d asen …£a wce…£ Necc, i ayt n Israil.  
\v 3 KuŇô amcan min xef …£a te…õjen tŇôeqqa n uŠłćar nwem, aqa wci…£ awem t i kenniw, am mammec i ssiwŇôe…£ Necc ak-d Musa. \x ‚óė \xo 1:3 \xt A…õwd. 11:24; Yac. 14:9\x*  
\v 4 Tammurt nwem ad tiŇôi zi ŇôexŇôa aŇô Lubnan-a, aŇô i…£zar ameqqran, i…£zar n LfuraŠĻ≠, marra tammurt n IŠł•ittiyyen aŇô ŇėebŠł•ar Ameqqran \add …£ar Ňô…£arb\add* mani t…£e«ßi tfuct. \f ‚óľ \fr 1:4 \ft \+fk ŇėebŠł•ar Ameqqran\ft  - ni…£ ‚ÄėIll Ameqqran‚Äô. ŇėebŠł•ar-a qqaren as di Arif ‚ÄėŇėebŠł•ar AmeŠļďyan‚Äô u isem nnes n jdid aqa-t ‚ÄėIll Agrakal‚Äô.\f*  
\v 5 UŇôa d ijj war izemmar ad iqqim ibedd zzat i wudem nnec marra ussan n tudart nnec. Am mammec d ayi tu…£a ak-d Musa, ad iŇôi…£ uŇôa akidek. Necc war dayek semmŠł•e…£ ni…£ ad cek ttejji…£. \x ‚óė \xo 1:5 \xt A…õwd. 31:6, 8; ∆źbr. 13:5, 6\x*  
\v 6 IŇôi d aryaz u iŇôi tmeŠł•Šłćed, minzi cek ad tarred Ňôgens-a ad iŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠ef tammurt d Ňôwart, \add tammurt nni\add* x Necc jju«ße…£ i Ňôejdud nsen ad asen tt wce…£. \x ‚óė \xo 1:6 \xt A…õwd. 31:23\x*  
\v 7 IŇôi waha d aryaz u iŇôi tmeŠł•Šłćed, maŠł•end ad teŠł•Šłćid ad tegged marra Ccari…õa nni d ac yumur Musa, amsexxar inu. War \add xas\add* ttŠł•eyyed \add …£ar\add* yefus uŇôa \add …£ar\add* uzeŇômaŠłć, maŠł•end ad tegged s Ňôe…õqeŇô mani ma i …£a traŠł•ed. \x ‚óė \xo 1:7 \xt A…õwd. 5:32; 28:14\x*  
\v 8 War ttejji ca adlis n Ccari…õa-ya ad ac ittwakkes x yiŇôes nnec, maca xarreŠĻ£ dayes ass d «ßiŇôet, maŠł•end ad teŠł•ŠłćiŠłć ad tegged ammu nican am mammec marra min dayes tura, minzi \add xenni\add* i …£a tfeŇôŠł•ed deg webrid nnec uca ad tt tegged s Ňôe…õqeŇô. \x ‚óė \xo 1:8 \xt Izhd. 1:2\x*  
\v 9 Ma war d ac t nni…£? IŇôi d aryaz u iŇôi tmeŠł•Šłćed, war ttegg ∑ed u war ttejji ad i…õgez wuŇô nnec, minzi SIDI, AREBBI nnec, aqa-t akidek qa…õ mani ma i …£a traŠł•ed.‚ÄĚ   
\m
\v 10 Uca yumur Yacuwa i imeŠł•Šłćayen n Ňôgens, inna:  
\v 11 ‚ÄúUyurem x ŇôwesŠĻ≠ n ŇômargeŠł• n Ňô…õeskar uca umur Ňôgens, inim \add asen\add*: ‚ÄėSwejdet Ňôe…õweńć i yixef nwem, minzi awarni i tŇôata n wussan ad teŠļďwam L‚ÄôUrdun-a, Šł•ima ad tadfem …£ar temmurt i d awem …£a iwc SIDI, AREBBI nwem, d Ňôwart uca ad tt teksim d Ňôwart.‚Äô‚ÄĚ   
\m
\v 12 IssiweŇô Yacuwa ak-d Irubiniyyen d Ijadiyyen u ak-d wezyen n teqbińć n Manassa, inna:  
\v 13 ‚Äú∆źeqŇôet x wawaŇô nni x i d awem yumur Musa, amsexxar n SIDI, umi inna awem: ‚ÄėSIDI, AREBBI nwem, iwca awem arraŠł•et uca iwca awem tammurt-a.  
\v 14 Tim…£arin nwem, iŠł•enjiren nwem d Ňôebhayem nwem ad qqimen di temmurt i d awem iwca Musa x ujemmaŠłć n L‚ÄôUrdun uca kenniw ad teŠļďwam tŠł•ezzmem zzat i wudem n aytmatwem, marra ayt n bu-te…£ruŠłćt imeŠł•Šłćen, uca kenniw ad asen tewcem afus,  
\v 15 aŇô …£a yewc SIDI arraŠł•et i aytmatwem, am \add tu…£a iwca i\add* kenniw, uca uŇôa d nitni ad ŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠fen tammurt i d asen iwca SIDI, AREBBI nwem, d Ňôwart. \add Xenni\add* ad i…õeddeŇô ad dd-tdewŇôem …£ar temmurt tenni d Ňôwart nwem uca ad twartem min d awem iwca Musa, amsexxar n SIDI, x ujemmaŠłć n L‚ÄôUrdun manis dd-tneqqar tfuct.‚ÄĚ   
\m
\v 16 Nitni arrin-dd x Yacuwa, nnan: ‚ÄúMarra min xef i d ane…£ tumured, ad t negg u mani ma i d ane…£ …£a tessekked, ad nuyur.  
\v 17 Ammu nican am mammec nesŇôa …£ar Musa, ad …£arek nseŇô. M…£ir iŇôi ad kik yiŇôi SIDI, AREBBI nnec, am mammec tu…£a i«ßa ak-d Musa!  
\v 18 KuŇô aryaz nni i …£a i…õŠĻ£an Ňôumur nnec u war ixs ad iseŇô i wawaŇôen nnec …£ar marra min d as …£a tumured, ad ittwane…£. IŇôi waha d aryaz u iŇôi tmeŠł•Šłćed!‚ÄĚ   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 2
\s1 RaŠł•ab d tnayen n ibergagen  
\m
\v 1 Yacuwa, mmis n Nun, issekk zi CiŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠im tnayen n yeryazen maŠł•end ad bergagen s tnuffra, inna: ‚ÄúUyurem, xzarem tammurt d AriŠł•a!‚ÄĚ Ff…£en, iwŠłćen …£ar taddart n ict n tem…£art n farq-cc…£eŇô, qqaren as RaŠł•ab, uca ssensen din.  
\v 2 Xebbaren t i uje«ßid n AriŠł•a, nnan: ‚ÄúXzar, di¬†«ßiŇôet-a usin-dd danita ca n yeryazen n ayt n Israil, Šł•ima ad bergagen di temmurt.‚ÄĚ  
\v 3 Issekk uje«ßid n AriŠł•a …£ar RaŠł•ab maŠł•end ad as inin: ‚ÄúSuffe…£-dd iryazen i dd yudfen …£ar taddart nnem, minzi usin-dd, Šł•ima ad ksin Ňôexbar x min ittemsaran di marra tammurt.‚ÄĚ  
\v 4 Aqa tessidef tem…£art tnayen n yeryazen nni uca tessnuffar i-ten. Tenna: ‚ÄúS tidett, iryazen usin-dd …£ari, maca war ssine…£ manis nitni.  
\v 5 Umi ttwabell…õent tewwura \add n tendint\add* …£ar uweŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠u n ta«ßest, ff…£en yeryazen. Necc war ssine…£ mani uyuren yeryazen \add nni\add*. ŠłĆfarem ten de…£ya, xenni tzemmarem ad xasen tŠł•artem.‚ÄĚ   
\m
\v 6 \add Maca\add* nettat tessge…õ…õed i-ten x tzeqqa uca tessnuffar i-ten sadu i…£eddiwen n tiffest nni tu…£a ttwassarsen i nettat x tzeqqa.  
\v 7 Tu…£a ten Šłćeffaren yeryazen x webrid n L‚ÄôUrdun aŇô imucan n uŠļďekkwu uca awarni Ňôami ff…£en inni tu…£a ten iŠłćeffaren, bell…õen xasen tawwart.  
\v 8 QbeŇô i …£a ŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠ŠĻ£en, tge…õ…õed \add RaŠł•ab\add* …£arsen …£ar tzeqqa,  
\v 9 tenna asen: ‚ÄúNecc ssne…£, aqa SIDI iwca awem tammurt-a u belli tigg ∑udi zzaywem tewŠłća-dd xane…£ u marra imezda…£ n temmurt fesyen deg wudem nwem.  
\v 10 Ma…£ar neccin nesŇôa, mammec issiŠļďe…£ SIDI aman n ŇėebŠł•ar n Telga deg wudem nwem umi dd-teff…£em zi MiŠĻ£ra, uca \add nesŇôa …õawed\add* min teggim ak-d SiŠł•un d ∆źuj, tnayen n ije«ßiden n Imuriyyen, inni tu…£a a…£irin i L‚ÄôUrdun, inni tŠł•arrmem u tŠĶČtteŠł•Šł•am.\x ‚óė \xo 2:10 \xt Uf. 14:21; ŇėxŇô. 21:24, 34; Yac. 4:23\x*  
\v 11 \add Umi\add* nesŇôa aya, ifsiy wuŇô nne…£, u war iqqim ca buŠł•beŇô iddar di ca n yeryaz di ssibbet nwem, minzi SIDI, AREBBI nwem, d AREBBI, sennej deg ujenna d \add da\add* swadday x temmurt. \x ‚óė \xo 2:11 \xt A…õwd. 4:39\x*  
\v 12 Ňėexxu \add xenni\add*, jja«ßem ayi …£ar SIDI, minzi necc ggi…£ zzaywem s tamexsiwt icewwaren, aqa uŇôa d kenniw ad teggem s tmexsiwt icewwaren ak-d \add Ňôa«ß n\add* taddart n baba u wcem ayi ijj n we…õŇôam n Ňôaman \add nwem\add*,  
\v 13 aqa kenniw ad tejjem baba d yemma, aytma d suyŠĶČtma ak-d marra min i«ßan nsen, ad ddaren u belli kenniw ad tfekkem Ňôe…õmurat nne…£ zi Ňômewt.‚ÄĚ   
\m
\v 14 Arrin-dd xas yeryazen: ‚ÄúMaŇôa war tefŠłćiŠł•em tamesŇôact nne…£, ad immet Ňôe…õmar nne…£ deg wemcan nwem. Uca ad imsar xmi d ane…£ …£a iwc SIDI tammurt\add -a\add*, ad am nesscen tamexsiwt icewwaren d Ňôaman \add nne…£\add*.‚ÄĚ   
\m
\v 15 Xas uca tseyyeb i-ten tem…£art s yijj n wes…£un zi Ňôkazi, minzi tu…£a taddart nnes …£ar ŇôŠł•iŠłć \add n barra\add* n wecbar \add n tendint\add* uca tu…£a tzedde…£ deg wecbar \add n tendint\add*. *   
\b  
\m
\v 16 Nettat tenna asen: ‚ÄúFf…£em …£ar idurar, maŠł•end inni i kenniw iŠłćeffaren war xawem Šł•arrten u ffarem dinni tŇôata n wussan aŇô …£a …õeqben inni \add kenniw\add* iŠłćeffaren. Awarni man aya tzemmarem ad tmen…õem abrid nwem.‚ÄĚ  
\v 17 Iryazen nnan as: ‚ÄúAd niŇôi nettwassizdeg zi tja«ßit-a i d ane…£ teggid ad tt nejja«ß,  
\v 18 \add ila maŇôa ad tegged ammu:\add* Xzar, xmi i …£a nadef …£ar temmurt, ittxeŠĻ£ŠĻ£a ad tegged as…£un-a azegg ∑a…£ imuden i zi d ane…£ tseyybed …£ar Ňôkazi, uca ad tessmuned babam d yemmam d aytmam d marra Ňôa«ß n babam …£arem di taddart nnem.  
\v 19 \add Maca\add* qa…õ wi …£a iff…£en zi tewwura n taddart nnem, ad iŇôin idammen nnes x uze«ßif nnes, u neccin ad niŇôi nettwassizdeg zzaysen, \add maca\add* qa…õ wenni akidem …£a iqqimen di taddart, idammen nnes ad iŇôin x uze«ßif nne…£ maŇôa \add ca n yijj\add* ad xas issars afus. \x ‚óė \xo 2:19 \xt Mt. 27:25\x*  
\v 20 MaŇôa cem tessuff…£ed tamesŇôact nne…£, \add xenni\add* ad niŇôi nettwassizdeg \add …õawed\add* zi tja«ßit i d ane…£ teggid ad am nejju«ß i cem.‚ÄĚ  
\v 21 Nettat tarra-dd xasen: ‚Äú∆źlaŠł•sab awaŇôen nwem, ammu \add i …£a yiŇôi\add*!‚ÄĚ \add Xenni\add* tejja i-ten ad uyuren uca tcedd as…£un azegg ∑a…£ …£ar Ňôkazi. \x ‚óė \xo 2:21 \xt Ica. 1:18\x*   
\m
\v 22 Uyuren nitni uca iwŠłćen …£ar wedrar uca qqimen dinni tŇôata n wussan, aŇôami dd-…õeqben inni i ten iŠłćeffaren. Inni ten iŠłćeffaren tu…£a arezzun \add xasen\add* deg webrid marra, maca war \add ten\add* ufin.  
\v 23 \add Xenni\add* aregg ∑Šł•en-dd tnayen nni n yeryazen, hwan-dd zeg wedrar, Šļďwan-dd uca usin-dd …£ar Yacuwa, mmis n Nun, u Šł•ajan as marra min d asen imsaren.  
\v 24 Nnan i Yacuwa: ‚ÄúS tidett, SIDI igga ane…£ marra tammurt deg ifassen u \add …õawed\add* fesyen marra imezda…£ n temmurt di ssibbet nne…£.‚ÄĚ   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 3
\s1 AŠļďwi n L‚ÄôUrdun  
\m
\v 1 ∆Ēar tuffut zic, ikkar Yacuwa uca ksin iqiŠłćan nsen zi CiŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠im uca usin-dd …£ar L‚ÄôUrdun, netta d marra ayt n Israil, uca ssensen dinni qbeŇô i …£a Šļďwan.  
\v 2 Imsar awarni tŇôata n wussan, aqa imeŠł•Šłćayen uyuren x ŇôwesŠĻ≠ n ŇômargeŠł• n Ňô…õeskar  
\v 3 uca umuren Ňôgens, nnan: ‚ÄúXmi …£a tŠļďarem Ttabut n Ňė…õahd n SIDI, AREBBI nwem, uca ikehhanen Ilawiyyen arbun tt, \add xenni\add* uŇôa d kenniw ad temmuŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠yem zeg wemcam nwem, ad tt teŠłćfarem.  
\v 4 Maca ittxeŠĻ£ŠĻ£a ad t…õebbarem ttasi…õ …õŇôaŠł•aŇô i aŇôfayen n i…£a«ßen jar awem d netta, war …£ares tadsem. Ammu i …£a tessnem abrid i …£a tekkem, ma…£ar kenniw \add zic\add* …õemmarŠĻ£ war tekkim abrid-a, \add war i«ßi\add* iŠłćennaŠłć u \add war i«ßi\add* fariŠłćennaŠłć.‚ÄĚ   
\m
\v 5 Inna Yacuwa i Ňôgens: ‚ÄúQeddsem ixef nwem, minzi tiwecca ad igg SIDI Ňôe…õjayeb di ŇôwesŠĻ≠ nwem.‚ÄĚ  
\v 6 IssiweŇô Yacuwa \add …õawed\add* ak-d ikehhanen, inna: ‚ÄúSge…õ…õdem Ttabut n Ňė…õahd uca Šļďwam zzat i wudem n Ňôgens!‚ÄĚ Nitni ssge…õ…õden Ttabut n Ňė…õahd u izwaren …£ar zzat i wudem n Ňôgens.  
\v 7 Tu…£a SIDI inna i Yacuwa: ‚ÄúAss-a ad kkare…£ ad cek ssem…£are…£ zzat i tiŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠awin n marra Israil, maŠł•end marra ad ssnen, aqa Necc akidek i «ßi…£, am mammec i d ayi tu…£a ak-d Musa. \x ‚óė \xo 3:7 \xt Yac. 1:5\x*  
\v 8 Cek ad tumured ikehhanen inni yarebbun Ttabut n Ňė…õahd, ad tinid: ‚ÄėX minni i …£a tawŠłćem …£ar tma n waman n L‚ÄôUrdun, ad din tbeddem di L‚ÄôUrdun!‚Äô‚ÄĚ   
\m
\v 9 \add Xas uca\add* inna Yacuwa i ayt n Israil: ‚ÄúAsem-dd da u tesŇôem awaŇôen n SIDI, AREBBI nwem.‚ÄĚ  
\v 10 Uca inna Yacuwa: ‚ÄúS man aya ad tessnem, aqa ijj n Arebbi iddar aqa-t jar awem u Netta ad issuffe…£ ayt n Ken…õan d IŠł•ittiyyen d IŠł•iwiyyen d Ifariziyyen d Ijirjaciyyen d Imuriyyen d Iyabusiyyen zzat i tiŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠awin nwem zi Ňôwart nsen.  
\v 11 Xzarem, Ttabut n Ňė…õahd n Sidi n marra tammurt tezwar awem zzat i wudem nwem di L‚ÄôUrdun.  
\v 12 Ňėexxu \add xenni\add*, farnem ten…õac n yeryazen zi tqebbaŇô n Israil akidwem, ijj n weryaz zi kuŇô taqbińć.  
\v 13 Xmi iŠłćaren n ikehhanen, inni yarebbun Ttabut n SIDI, Sidi n marra tammurt, ad bedden deg waman n L‚ÄôUrdun, \add xenni\add* ad imsar aqa aman n L‚ÄôUrdun ad nqeŠłć…õen, aman i dd-ihekkwan zi sennej …£ar swadday, uca ad \add qqimen\add* bedden am yijj n we…£bar.‚ÄĚ \x ‚óė \xo 3:13 \xt Izhd. 114:3\x*  
\v 14 \add Ňėami\add* ikkes Ňôgens iqiŠłćan nnes Šł•ima ad iŠļďwa L‚ÄôUrdun, arbun ikehhanen Ttabut n Ňė…õahd zzat i wudem n Ňôgens. \x ‚óė \xo 3:14 \xt Ňėex. 7:45\x*  
\v 15 \add Umi\add* iwŠłćen iŠł•emmaŇôen n Ttabut …£ar L‚ÄôUrdun uca Šł•adan iŠłćaren n ikehhanen, inni yarbun Ttabut, x tma n waman - tu…£a L‚ÄôUrdun issfiy x marra tmewwa nnes di marra ussan n tmeyra - \x ‚óė \xo 3:15 \xt 1 Im. 12:16\x*  
\v 16 bedden waman nni dd-ihekkwan zi sennej. \add Aman\add* bedden nican am yijj n we…£bar igg ∑ej aŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠as, …£ar tendint n Adam tenni zzat i ŠĻĘartan. \add Ammu\add* i bedden \add waman\add* inni dd-ihekk ∑an …£ar swadday, …£ar ŇôebŠł•ar n ŇėewŠłća, …£ar ŇėebŠł•ar Ame«ßaŠł•, aqa ttwaqeŠłć…õen qa…õ. \add Xenni\add* iŠļďwa Ňôgens deg urendad n AriŠł•a.  
\v 17 Ikehhanen, inni yarbun Ttabut n Ňė…õahd n SIDI, bedden di¬†Ňôaman x ŇôaŠļďa…£, di ŇôwesŠĻ≠ n L‚ÄôUrdun \add umi\add* iŠļďwa marra Israil x ŇôaŠļďa…£ aŇôami ikemmeŇô marra Ňôgens aŠļďwi x L‚ÄôUrdun.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 4
\m
\v 1 Umi tu…£a ikemmeŇô marra Ňôgens aŠļďwi x L‚ÄôUrdun, imsar aqa SIDI issiweŇô ak-d Yacuwa, inna: \x ‚óė \xo 4:1 \xt Yac. 3:12\x*  
\v 2 ‚ÄúFarnem ten…õac n yeryazen zi¬†Ňôgens, ijjen weryaz zi kuŇô¬†taqbińć,  
\v 3 u tumured xasen, ini: ‚ÄėKsim ssa, zi¬†Ňôwest n L‚ÄôUrdun, zeg wemcan mani tu…£a bedden iŠłćaren n ikehhanen di Ňôaman, ten…õac n iŠļďra, ksim ten akidwem …£ar ujemmaŠłćin, ssarsem ten di ŇômargeŠł• n Ňô…õeskar mani …£a tessensem «ßiŇôet-a.‚Äô‚ÄĚ   
\m
\v 4 \add Xenni\add* iŇôa…£a Yacuwa ten…õac n yeryazen nni ifarn i-ten zeg ayt n Israil, ijj n weryaz zi kuŇô taqbińć,  
\v 5 uca Yacuwa inna asen: ‚ÄúUyurem zzat i wudem n Ttabut n SIDI, AREBBI nwem, …£ar ŇôwesŠĻ≠ n L‚ÄôUrdun uca ad iksi kuŇô aryaz i yixef nnes ijj n weŠļďru x te…£ruŠłćt nnes, …õlaŠł•sab Ňôqedd n tqebbaŇô n ayt n Israil,  
\v 6 Šł•ima ad yiŇôi aya d ict n Ňôe…õŇôamet jar awem. Minzi \add maŇôa\add* iŠł•enjiren nwem ad sseqsan, ad inin: ‚ÄėMin \add ixs ad inin\add* yeŠļďra-ya i kenniw?‚Äô,  
\v 7 \add xenni\add* kenniw ad asen tinim: ‚Äė\add Aqa-ten din\add* minzi nqeŠłć…õen waman n L‚ÄôUrdun zzat i wudem n Ttabut n Ňė…õahd n SIDI! ∆Ēar uŠļďwi x L‚ÄôUrdun nqeŠłć…õen waman n L‚ÄôUrdun uca iŠļďra-ya d ict n Ňôidaret i ayt n Israil \add di man aya\add* i Ňôebda.‚Äô‚ÄĚ \x ‚óė \xo 4:7 \xt Yac. 3:13\x*  
\v 8 Ayt n Israil ggin am mammec tu…£a yumur Yacuwa uca ksin ten…õac n iŠļďra zi ŇôwesŠĻ≠ n L‚ÄôUrdun, am mammec tu…£a issiweŇô SIDI …£ar Yacuwa, …õlaŠł•sab Ňôqedd n tqebbaŇô n ayt n Israil, uca ksin ten akidsen …£ar ujemmaŠłćin, …£ar ŇômargeŠł• mani tu…£a ssensen, uca ssarsen ten din.  
\v 9 Issars Yacuwa \add …õawed\add* ten…õac n iŠļďra di ŇôwesŠĻ≠ n L‚ÄôUrdun, deg wemcan mani tu…£a mmarsen iŠłćaren n ikehhanen, inni yarbun Ttabut n Ňė…õahd, u aqa aten …õad din aŇô ass-a.   
\m
\v 10 Ikehhanen, inni yarbun Ttabut, qqimen bedden di ŇôwesŠĻ≠ n L‚ÄôUrdun, aŇôami tu…£a ittwakemmeŇô min inna SIDI i Yacuwa maŠł•end ad t yini i Ňôgens …õlaŠł•sab marra min yumur Musa i Yacuwa, uca iqe«ßeq Ňôgens ssenni, iŠļďwa.  
\v 11 Umi tu…£a marra Ňôgens ikemmeŇô aŠļďwi, teŠļďwa Ttabut n SIDI ak-d ikehhanen zzat i wudem n Ňôgens.  
\v 12 Ayt n Rubin d ayt n Jad d wezyen n teqbińć n Manassa Šļďwan Šł•ezzmen i umen…£i zzat i wudem n ayt n Israil, am mammec tu…£a akidsen issiweŇô Musa. \x ‚óė \xo 4:12 \xt ŇėxŇô. 32:20, 29\x*  
\v 13 Tu…£a-ten …õŇôaŠł•aŇô di areb…õin-aŇôef \add n yeryazen\add*, Šł•ezzmen \add marra\add* i umen…£i. Nitni Šļďwan …£ar \add wazzay n\add* umen…£i zzat i wudem n SIDI, …£ar ŇôewŠłćat n AriŠł•a.  
\v 14 SIDI issem…£ar Yacuwa deg wass nni di tiŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠awin n marra Israil uca gg ∑eden zzayes am mammec tu…£a gg ∑eden zi Musa, marra ussan n tudart nnes. \x ‚óė \xo 4:14 \xt Yac. 3:7\x*   
\m
\v 15 SIDI issiweŇô ak-d Yacuwa, inna:  
\v 16 ‚ÄúUmur i ikehhanen, inni yarebbun Ttabut n Cchadet, ad ge…õ…õden zi L‚ÄôUrdun.‚ÄĚ  
\v 17 \add Xenni\add* yumur Yacuwa ikehhanen, inna: ‚ÄúGa…õ…õdem zi L‚ÄôUrdun …£ar sennej!‚ÄĚ  
\v 18 Umi ge…õ…õden ikehhanen, inni yarbun Ttabut n Ňė…õahd n SIDI, zi¬†ŇôwesŠĻ≠ n L‚ÄôUrdun u tu…£a tisi n iŠłćaren n ikehhanen …õad am mammec dd-ff…£en \add zeg waman\add*, imsar aqa aman n L‚ÄôUrdun dewŇôen …£ar wemcan nsen uca dewŇôen ssfayen x marra timmawin nnes am yiŠłćennaŠłć d fariŠłćennaŠłć.  
\v 19 Tu…£a Ňôgens ige…õ…õed zi L‚ÄôUrdun deg wass wiss …õecra deg uyur amezwaru uca wtin iqiŠłćan nsen di Jiljal, …£ar ccarq n AriŠł•a.   
\m
\v 20 Di Jiljal issbedd Yacuwa ten…õac n iŠļďra i tu…£a akidsen-dd iksin zi L‚ÄôUrdun.  
\v 21 Uca netta issiweŇô ak-d ayt n Israil, inna: ‚ÄúMaŇôa sseqsan tiwecca iŠł•enjiren nwem ibabaten nsen uca ad inin: ‚ÄėMin \add xsen ad inin\add* yeŠļďra-ya?‚Äô  
\v 22 \add xenni\add* ad t…õeŇômem i iŠł•enjiren nwem, ad tinim: ‚Äė\add Danita\add* iŠļďwa Israil L‚ÄôUrdun-a x ŇôaŠļďa…£,  
\v 23 minzi SIDI, AREBBI nwem, issiŠļďe…£ aman n L‚ÄôUrdun zzat i wudem nwem aŇôami teŠļďwam, am mammec i tu…£a igga SIDI, AREBBI nwem, \add …õawed\add* ak-d ŇėebŠł•ar n Telga nni issiŠļďe…£ zzat i wudem nne…£ aŇôami \add din\add* neŠļďwa, \x ‚óė \xo 4:23 \xt Uf. 14:21\x*  
\v 24 Šł•ima marra Ňôegnus x temmurt ad ssnen, aqa afus n SIDI ijhed, Šł•ima kenniw ad tegg ∑dem SIDI, AREBBI nwem, i Ňôebda.‚Äô‚ÄĚ   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 5
\s1 Axtan n Ňôgens di Jiljal  
\m
\v 1 Umi marra ije«ßiden n Imuriyyen \add i i«ßan\add* x tma n Ňô…£arb n L‚ÄôUrdun d marra ije«ßiden n ayt n Ken…õan \add i i«ßan\add* …£ar ŇôebŠł•ar, sŇôan, aqa SIDI issiŠļďe…£ aman n L‚ÄôUrdun zzat i wudem n ayt n Israil, aŇôami neŠļďwa …£ar ujemmaŠłćin, \add xenni\add* ifsiy wuŇô nsen u war daysen iqqim ca arruŠł• zzat i wudem n ayt n Israil.  
\v 2 Di Ňôweqt nni issiweŇô SIDI ak-d Yacuwa: ‚ÄúEgg i yixef nnec ifarricen n weŠļďru uca xten i ayt n Israil i twaŇôa wiss tnayen!‚ÄĚ \x ‚óė \xo 5:2 \xt Uf. 4:25\x*  
\v 3 \add Xenni\add* igga Yacuwa ifarricen n weŠļďru i yixef nnes uca ixten i ayt n Israil …£ar Jib…õa-Ha…õralut, \add aqa d ‚ÄėTawrirt n Ňėe…õdaŇôeyyat n Wextan‚Äô\add*.  
\v 4 Man aya d Ňôesbab i zi ixten i-ten Yacuwa: marra Ňôgens i tu…£a dd-iff…£en zi MiŠĻ£ra, \add marra\add* iwetman, \add ixs ad yini\add* marra i…õeskariyyen mmuten deg webrid di ŇôexŇôa awarni i wuffu…£ nsen zi MiŠĻ£ra.  
\v 5 Minzi marra Ňôgens nni dd-iff…£en, tu…£a-t ittwaxten, \add maca\add* marra Ňôgens nni dd-ittwaxeŇôqen deg webrid di ŇôexŇôa awarni i uffu…£ nsen zi MiŠĻ£ra, nitni war ttwaxetnen ca. \x ‚óė \xo 5:5 \xt Uf. 12:48\x*  
\v 6 Minzi areb…õin n isegg ∑usa gguren ayt n Israil di ŇôexŇôa aŇôami ittwahellek Ňôgens marra, marra i…õeskariyyen i tu…£a dd-iff…£en zi MiŠĻ£ra, inni tu…£a war isŇôin …£ar tmijja n SIDI \add d inni\add* tu…£a ijju«ß asen SIDI, war ten ittejji ca ad Šļďaren tammurt nni x tu…£a ijju«ß SIDI i Ňôejdud nsen ad asen tt iwc, ict n temmurt ifeyyŠłćen s u…£i d tamment. \x ‚óė \xo 5:6 \xt ŇėxŇô. 14:23\x*  
\v 7 IŠł•enjiren nsen inni issnekkar Netta deg wemcan nsen, d ina d inni tu…£a ixten Yacuwa, minzi nitni …£arsen …õad Ňôe…õdaŇôyet minzi war d asen xetnen deg webrid.  
\v 8 Umi kemmŇôen ad xten marra Ňôgens, imsar belli qqimen deg wemcan nsen di ŇômargeŠł• n Ňô…õeskar aŇôami ggenfan.  
\v 9 Inna SIDI i Yacuwa: ‚ÄúAss-a aqa kkse…£ xawem ŇôefŠłćiŠł•et n MiŠĻ£ra.‚ÄĚ \add X uyenni\add* qqaren as i wemcan nni Jiljal, aŇô ass-a.   
