\m  
\s1 Ta…£arŠĻ£t n Use…õdu - ‚ÄėManna‚Äô, a…£rum n ujenna, ibedd  
\m
\v 10 Wtin ayt n Israil iqiŠłćan nsen di Jiljal uca sswejden \add Ta…£arŠĻ£t n\add* Use…õdu deg wass arbe…õŠĻ≠ac n uyur \add nni\add*, di¬†«ßiŇôet, di ŇôewŠłćat n AriŠł•a. \x ‚óė \xo 5:10 \xt Uf. 12:6\x*  
\v 11 Nitni ccin a…£rum bŇôa antun d te…£wawin icennfen zi Ňô…£i«ßet n temmurt, zi tiwecca awarni i \add Ta…£arŠĻ£t n\add* Use…õdu, deg wass nni simant nnes. \x ‚óė \xo 5:11 \xt Uf. 12:39; Lawi 2:14\x*  
\v 12 Tiwecca nnes, awarni Ňôami ccin zi Ňô…£i«ßet n temmurt, inneqŠłće…õ manna. Ssenni war iqqim …õad ‚Äėmanna‚Äô i ayt n Israil. Deg usegg ∑as nni ccin zi Ňô…£i«ßet n temmurt n Ken…õan.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Yacuwa iŠļďra Ameqqran n Ňô…õeskar n SIDI  
\m
\v 13 Umi tu…£a i«ßa Yacuwa zzat i AriŠł•a, issge…õ…õed tiŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠awin nnes, uca xzar, tu…£a ijj n weryaz ibedd zzates, …£ares ssif nnes deg ufus nnes. Yacuwa iruŠł• …£ares inna as: ‚ÄúCek ma zzayne…£ ni…£ zeg i…£rimen nne…£?‚ÄĚ \x ‚óė \xo 5:13 \xt Uf. 23:23\x*  
\v 14 Netta yarra-dd: ‚ÄúLla, minzi necc d akumandar n Ňô…õeskar n SIDI. Necc Ňôexxu i dd-usi…£!‚ÄĚ Uca iwŠłća Yacuwa x u…£embub nnes …£ar temmurt, yuŠłćar, uca inna as: ‚ÄúMin ixs ad yini Sidi inu i umsexxar nnes?‚ÄĚ  
\v 15 \add Xenni\add* inna akumandar n Ňô…õeskar n SIDI i Yacuwa: ‚ÄúKkes tisiŇôa nnec zeg iŠłćaren nnec, minzi amcan i xef tbedded d amqeddas \add i i«ßa\add*.‚ÄĚ Uca amenni i igga Yacuwa. \x ‚óė \xo 5:15 \xt Uf. 3:5\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 6
\s1 AweŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠u n AriŠł•a  
\m
\v 1 AriŠł•a tu…£a teqqen \add tiwwura nnes\add* nican zzat i wudem n ayt n Israil. UŇôa d ijj war izemmar ad iffe…£, uŇôa d ijj war izemmar ad \add din\add* yadef.  
\v 2 \add Xenni\add* inna SIDI i Yacuwa: ‚ÄúXzar, Necc ggi…£ ac AriŠł•a ak-d uje«ßid nnes, ayt n bu-te…£ruŠłćt imeŠł•Šłćen, deg ufus nnec.  
\v 3 IttxeŠĻ£ŠĻ£a kenniw ad tennŠłćem i tendint. Marra i…õeskariyyen ad nnŠłćen i tendint ict n twaŇôa. Amya i …£a teggem setta n wussan.  
\v 4 Seb…õa n ikehhanen ad izwaren zzat i Ttabut ad arbun seb…õa n waccawen n icarri i usŇôiwŇôew. Deg wass wiss seb…õa ad tennŠłćem i tendint seb…õa n twaŇôawin u \add xenni\add* ad suŠłćen ikehhanen deg waccawen n icarri.  
\v 5 Xmi …£a yiŇôi ijj n usuŠłći d azirar deg yicc n usŇôiwŇôew u kenniw ad tesŇôem ŇôŠł•ess-a n usuŠłći deg uyicc n icarri, \add xenni\add* ad yarreŠļď Ňôgens imun s t…£uyyit deg ujenna. Xas uca ad iwŠłća ŇôŠł•iŠłć n tendint uca ad xas iŠļďwa Ňôgens, kuŇô ijj n weryaz ad yuyur nican …£ar zzat.‚ÄĚ   
\m
\v 6 \add Xenni\add* iŇôa…£a Yacuwa, mmis n Nun, x ikehhanen, inna asen: ‚ÄúKsim kenniw Ttabut n Ňė…õahd u ttejjem seb…õa n ikehhanen ad izwaren …£ar zzat i wudem n Ttabut n SIDI ad arbun seb…õa n waccawen n icarri i usŇôiwŇôew.‚ÄĚ  
\v 7 Nnan i Ňôgens: ‚ÄúŠļíwam u tennŠłćem i tendint. Jjem i…õeskariyyen s ŇôesnaŠł• ad Šļďwan zzat i wudem n Ttabut n SIDI.‚ÄĚ   
\m
\v 8 Imsar am mammec tu…£a inna Yacuwa i Ňôgens. Seb…õa n ikehhanen tu…£a arebbun seb…õa n waccawen n icarri i usŇôiwŇôew uca Šļďwan zzat i wudem n SIDI, suŠłćen deg waccawen n icarri uca Ttabut n Ňė…õahd n SIDI teggur awarni asen.  
\v 9 \add Iryazen\add* iŠł•ezzmen s ŇôesnaŠł• izwaren zzat i wudem n ikehhanen nni isuŠłćen deg waccawen n icarri u x Šłćeffar n Ttabut yusa-dd u…£ezdis aneggaru \add n Ňô…õeskar\add*, am gguren, ttsuŠłćen nitni deg waccawen n icarri.   
\m
\v 10 Yacuwa aqa yumur Ňôgens, inna ‚ÄúWar ttes…£uyyum, war ttejjim tmijja nwem ad as iseŇô Šł•ed, war dd-itteffe…£ uŇôa d ijj n wawaŇô zeg uqemmum nwem aŇô ass nni d awem …£a ini…£: ‚ÄėS…£uyyem!‚Äô \add Xenni\add* ad tes…£uyyem i umen…£i.‚ÄĚ  
\v 11 Xas uca yejja Ttabut n SIDI ad tenneŠłć i tendint, ict n twaŇôa tenneŠłć as-dd. \add Xenni\add* dewŇôen …£ar ŇômargeŠł• n Ňô…õeskar, ssensen di ŇômargeŠł•.  
\v 12 Tiwecca nnes …£ar tuffut n zic ikkar Yacuwa uca arbun ikehhanen Ttabut n SIDI.  
\v 13 Seb…õa n ikehhanen nni tu…£a yarebbun seb…õa n waccawen n icarri i usŇôiwŇôew zzat i wudem n Ttabut n SIDI, qqimen gguren, suŠłćen deg waccawen n icarri u \add iryazen\add* iŠł•ezzmen s ŇôesnaŠł• izwaren …£ar zzat u x Šłćeffar n Ttabut n SIDI iŠłćfar u…£ezdis aneggaru \add n Ňô…õeskar\add*, am \add qqimen\add* gguren am ttsuŠłćen deg waccawen n icarri.  
\v 14 Deg wass wiss tnayen nnŠłćen \add …õawed\add* ict n twaŇôa i tendint uca dewŇôen …£ar ŇômargeŠł• n Ňô…õeskar. Ammu i ggin setta n wussan.  
\v 15 Deg wass wiss seb…õa, imsar, aqa kkaren zic, umi iŠĻ£beŠł• ŇôŠł•aŇô, uca nnŠłćen ammu seb…õa n twaŇôawin i tendint. Deg wass nni waha nnŠłćen i tendint seb…õa n twaŇôawin.  
\v 16 Uca imsar …£ar twaŇôa wiss seb…õa umi suŠłćen ikehhanen deg waccawen n icarri, aqa Yacuwa inna i Ňôgens: ‚ÄúS…£uyyem, minzi SIDI igga awem tandint deg ufus!  
\v 17 Tandint ad tŠĶČttwaŠł•arrem i SIDI, tandint d marra min dayes. M…£ir tam…£art n farq-cc…£eŇô RaŠł•ab waha d marra inni …£ares i«ßan di taddart nnes ad qqimen ddaren, minzi nettat tessnuffar x ireqqasen nni tu…£a nessekk.  
\v 18 Šł§Šłćam ixef nwem zi marra min ittwaŠł•arrmen, maŠł•end kenniw war teddikkwiŇôem d ayt n ŇôeŠł•ram \add am\add* teksim \add ca\add* n min i«ßan d ŇôeŠł•ram u ad tarrem ŇômargeŠł• n Ňô…õeskar n Israil d ŇôeŠł•ram u ad t t…£eŠłćŇôem d arrŠļďiyet.  
\v 19 Marra nnuqart d wure…£ d Ňôeqcu…õ n nnŠł•as d wuzzaŇô, \add marra aya\add* d amqeddas i SIDI uca ad t tessidfem deg wexxam n txubay n SIDI.‚ÄĚ \x ‚óė \xo 6:19 \xt ŇėxŇô. 31:54\x*  
\v 20 Xas uca is…£uy Ňôgens i umen…£i uca suŠłćen deg waccawen n icarri. Uca imsar, umi isŇôa Ňôgens ŇôŠł•ess n usuŠłći deg uyicc n icarri, aqa Ňôgens yarreŠļď deg ict n t…£uyyit deg ujenna u ŇôŠł•iŠłć n tendint ihdem u Ňôgens ige…õ…õed, yudef …£ar tendint, kuŇô ijj n weryaz yuyur nican …£ar zzat, uca ŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠fen nitni tandint. \x ‚óė \xo 6:20 \xt ∆źbr. 11:30\x*  
\v 21 Šł§arrmen marra min i«ßan di tendint i ŇôŠł•ukm s ŇôeqŠłće…õ n ssif, zeg iryazen aŇô tim…£arin, zeg iŠł•ramen aŇô iwessura, aŇô afunas, u«ßi d we…£yuŇô.  
\v 22 Inna Yacuwa i tnayen n yeryazen nni tu…£a ittbergagen tammurt: ‚ÄúAdfem …£ar taddart n tem…£art n farq-cc…£eŇô, u ssuff…£em tam…£art nni ak-d marra min …£ares, am mammec kenniw i d as tejju«ßem.‚ÄĚ \x ‚óė \xo 6:22 \xt Yac. 2:14; ∆źbr. 11:31\x*  
\v 23 \add Xenni\add* udfen ibŇôi…£en, ibergagen, uca ssuff…£en-dd RaŠł•ab ak-d babas d yemmas d aytmas d marra min i«ßan nnes. Ssuff…£en marra Ňôa«ß nnes uca ggin asen mani …£a qqimen barra i ŇômargeŠł• n Ňô…õeskar n Israil.  
\v 24 SscemŠłćen tandint d marra min dayes s tmessi. M…£ir nnuqart d wure…£ d Ňôeqcu…õ n nnŠł•as d wuzzaŇô, ssidfen ten …£ar wexxam n txubay di Taddart n SIDI.  
\v 25 RaŠł•ab, tam…£art n farq-cc…£eŇô d \add Ňôa«ß n\add* taddart n babas d marra min i«ßan nnes, ijja i-ten Yacuwa ad ddaren. U nettat tzedde…£ di ŇôwesŠĻ≠ n Israil aŇô ass-a, minzi tu…£a tessnuffar x ireqqasen i tu…£a issekk Yacuwa, Šł•ima ad bergagen tammurt.  
\v 26 Di Ňôweqt nni ijju«ß Yacuwa, inna: ‚ÄúAryaz nni i …£a issbedd AriŠł•a …õawed ad yiŇôi ittwan…õeŇô zzat i wudem n SIDI. Ad as yegg dsas nnes di tareŠļďŠļďit n umenzu nnes, ad issbedd tiwwura nnes di tareŠļďŠļďit n mmis amaŠļďuŠļď.‚ÄĚ \x ‚óė \xo 6:26 \xt 1 Ij. 16:34\x*  
\v 27 \add Ammu\add* i tu…£a SIDI ak-d Yacuwa, uca Ňôexbar ikka marra tammurt.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 7
\s1 Ddenb n ∆źaxan  
\m
\v 1 Ayt n Israil …£eccen ak-d min i«ßan ittwaŠł•arrmen \add i uteŠł•Šł•i\add*. ∆źaxan, mmis n Karmi, mmis n Zabdi, mmis n ZaraŠł•, zi teqbińć n Yahuda, iksi ca zi min ittwaŠł•arrmen \add i uteŠł•Šł•i\add*. \add Xenni\add* yar…£a we…£Šłćab n SIDI x ayt n Israil. \x ‚óė \xo 7:1 \xt Yac. 22:20; 1 Im. 2:7\x*   
\m
\v 2 Yacuwa issekk iryazen zi AriŠł•a …£ar ∆źay i i«ßan …£ar Bayt-Awin, …£ar ccarq n Bayt-Il. Netta issiweŇô akidsen, inna: ‚ÄúGa…õ…õdem, bergagem tammurt!‚ÄĚ Iryazen ff…£en u bergagen x ∆źay.  
\v 3 \add Umi\add* dd-…õeqben …£ar Yacuwa, nnan as: ‚ÄúNhŇôa ma ige…õ…õed din marra Ňôgens. Ejj ad ge…õ…õden din …õŇôaŠł•aŇô aŇôfayen ni…£ teŇôt-aŇôaf n yeryazen Šł•ima ad …£eŇôben x ∆źay. War dd-ttiwyed ca dinni marra Ňôgens, minzi nitni aqa aten di drus.  
\v 4 \add Ammu\add* i ge…õ…õden zi Ňôgens …õŇôaŠł•aŇô teŇôt-aŇôaf n yeryazen, \add maca\add* nitni arewŇôen zzat i wudem n yeryazen n ∆źay.  
\v 5 Iryazen n ∆źay n…£in zzaysen setta u-tŇôatin n yeryazen uca Šłćfaren ten zi zzat n wudem n tewwart aŇô Cabarim uca …£eŇôben xasen deg uhekkwu. \add Xenni\add* ifsiy wuŇô n Ňôgens, idweŇô am waman.   
\m
\v 6 Yacuwa icarreg arruŠłć nnes, iwŠłća x u…£embub nnes …£ar temmurt zzat i Ttabut n SIDI, aŇô «ßiŇôet, netta d im…£aren n Israil, uca nitni ssuyusen ucaŇô x uze«ßif nsen.  
