\v 10 \add Xenni\add* inna SIDI i Yacuwa: ‚ÄúKkar, mayemmi \add da\add* tmedded ammu x u…£embub nnec …£ar temmurt?  
\v 11 Aqa Israil ixŠłća uca nitni …õeddan Ňė…õahd inu nni x d asen umure…£. Ksin \add …õawed\add* zi min i«ßan ittwaŠł•arrmen \add i uteŠł•Šł•i\add*, ucaren \add …õawed\add*, ssxarrqen \add …õawed\add* uca ssarsen \add aya\add* \add …õawed\add* …£ar Ňôeqcu…õ nsen.  
\v 12 \add X uya\add* war zemmaren ayt n Israil ad qqimen bedden zzat i wudem n Ňô…õedyan nsen. Ad arrin a…õrur …£ar wudem n Ňô…õedyan nsen \add maŠł•end ad arewŇôen\add*, minzi nitni dewŇôen ttwaŠł•arrmen \add qa…õ\add* i lŠł•ukm. Necc war kiwem ttiŇôi…£ …õad, maŇôa war tekksem zi ŇôwesŠĻ≠ nwem min ittwaŠł•arrmen \add i uteŠł•Šł•i\add*.  
\v 13 Kkar, sqeddes Ňôgens, ad tinid: ‚ÄėSqeddsem ixef nwem i tiwecca, minzi ammu i iqqar SIDI, AREBBI n Israil: Aqa din ca min ittwaŠł•arrmen \add i uteŠł•Šł•i\add* di ŇôwesŠĻ≠ nwem, Israil! War tzemmared ad tessbedded Ňô…õedyan nnec, aŇô …£a tekksem zi ŇôwesŠĻ≠ nwem min ittwaŠł•arrmen \add i uteŠł•Šł•i\add*.  
\v 14 Tiwecca ad dd-tqarrbem, \add ad tiŇôim tŠĶČttwasettfem\add* …õlaŠł•sab tiqebbaŇô nwem uca \add xenni\add* ad dd-tqarreb teqbińć nni i…õe«ßem SIDI, …õlaŠł•sab Ňôa«ßat \add nnes\add* u Ňôa«ß i …£a i…õe«ßem SIDI ad dd-iqarreb …õlaŠł•sab \add Ňôa«ßat n\add* tudrin \add nnes\add* uca \add Ňôa«ß n\add* taddart nni i …£a i…õe«ßem SIDI ad dd-iqarreb \add am ttwasettfen nitni\add* …õlaŠł•sab \add iryazen\add* ibŇôi…£en \add nsen\add*.  
