\c 8
\s1 A…£elleb x ∆źay  
\m
\v 1 \add Xenni\add* inna SIDI i Yacuwa: ‚ÄúWar ttegg ∑ed, war ttejji ad i…õgez wuŇô nnec. Ksi akidek marra Ňôgens n Ňô…õeskar, kkar, tuyured …£ar ∆źay! Xzar, Necc ggi…£ aje«ßid n ∆źay d Ňôgens nnes d tendint nnes d temmurt nnes deg ufus nnec. \x ‚óė \xo 8:1 \xt A…õwd. 1:21; 7:18\x*  
\v 2 Cek ad tegged ak-d ∆źay u ak-d uje«ßid nnes am mammec teggid ak-d AriŠł•a u ak-d uje«ßid nnes, ad teksim m…£ir takeccaŠłćt d Ňôebhayem waha i yixef nwem. Egg deg we…õrur n tendint ijn n Ňôfex.‚ÄĚ \x ‚óė \xo 8:2 \xt A…õwd. 20:14; Yac. 6:21\x*¬†¬†*   
