\v 3 \add Xas uca\add* ikkar Yacuwa ak-d marra Ňôgens n Ňô…õeskar Šł•ima ad ige…õ…õed …£ar ∆źay. IxŠłćar Yacuwa teŇôt-aŇôaf n yeryazen, ayt n bu-te…£ruŠłćt imeŠł•Šłćen, uca issekk i-ten s¬†«ßiŇôet  
\v 4 uca yumur i-ten, inna: ‚ÄúXzarem, ad teggem Ňôfex …£ar we…õŇôuŇô n tendint. War tigg ∑ejem aŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠as x tendint u iŇôim tŠł•ezzmem.  
\v 5 Necc ad dd-qarrbe…£ …£ar tendint ak-d marra Ňôgens. Ad imsar maŇôa ff…£en i umsagar akidne…£ am \add twaŇôat\add* tamezwarut, \add xenni\add* ad zzaysen narweŇô zzat i wudem nsen.  
