\v 9 \add Xenni\add* issekk i-ten Yacuwa uca nitni ggin Ňôfex uca qqimen jar Bayt-Il d ∆źay, …£ar Ňô…£arb x ∆źay. Yacuwa issens «ßiŇôet nni di ŇôwesŠĻ≠ n Ňôgens.  
