\v 11 Marra Ňôgens n Ňô…õeskar, inni kis i«ßan, iffe…£-dd uca nitni qarrben-dd uca iwŠłćen aŇô qibańć i tendint. Nitni wtin iqiŠłćan nsen …£ar ccamal n¬†∆źay. Tu…£a \add din\add* ict n te…£zurt jar as-dd d ∆źay.  
\v 12 Iksi netta …õŇôaŠł•aŇô xemsa-aŇôaf n yeryazen uca igga asen Ňôfex jar Bayt-Il d ∆źay, …£ar Ňô…£arb n tendint.  
\v 13 Ssbedden Ňôgens, ze…õma marra Ňô…õeskar …£ar ccamal n tendint, uca a…£ezdis aneggaru \add n Ňô…õeskar\add* …£ar Ňô…£arb n tendint. Yacuwa iruŠł• «ßiŇôet nni …£ar ŇôwesŠĻ≠ n ŇôewŠłća n te…£zurt.   
