\v 14 \add Umi\add* iŠļďra-ya uje«ßid n ∆źay, qe«ßqen uca kkaren zic. Ff…£en iryazen n tendint i umsagar ak-d Israil, i umen…£i, netta ak-d marra Ňôgens nnes, …£ar wazzay \add n umen…£i\add* zzat i wudem n ŇėewŠłća. Maca netta war issin belli tu…£a ggin as ijj n Ňôfex …£ar we…õrur n tendint.  
\v 15 Yacuwa d marra Israil ggin axmi jjin ixef nsen ad ttwawten qibańć nsen uca arewŇôen x webrid n ŇôexŇôa.  
\v 16 Marra Ňôgens i tu…£a i«ßan di tendint Ňôa…£an ten Šł•ima ad ten Šłćfaren. ŠłĆfaren Yacuwa uca dewŇôen igg ∑ejen x tendint.  
\v 17 UŇôa d ijj n weryaz war iqqim di ∆źay ni…£ di Bayt-Il, wenni war dd-iffi…£en ca i weŠłćfar awarni i Israil, uca nitni jjin tandint tarzem uca qqimen Šłćeffaren \add ayt n\add* Israil.   
