\v 18 \add Xenni\add* issiweŇô SIDI ak-d Yacuwa: ‚ÄúSwiŠļďŠļďeŠłć aŠł•ric nni deg ufus nnec …£ar¬†∆źay, minzi Necc ad wce…£ tandint deg ufus nnec.‚ÄĚ \add Xenni\add* isswiŠļďŠļďeŠłć Yacuwa aŠł•ric nni deg ufus nnes …£ar tendint. \f ‚óľ \fr 8:18 \ft \+fk Necc ad wce…£ tandint deg ufus nnec\ft  - s T…õibranit ‚ÄėNecc ad tt wce…£ deg ufus nnec‚Äô.\f*  
\v 19 \add Xenni\add* ikkar u…£ezdis aneggaru \add n Ňô…õeskar\add* de…£ya uca umi isarreŠł• \add Yacu…õa\add* afus nnes, bdan ad azzŇôen uca iwŠłćen …£ar tendint uca ŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠fen tt. Ggin t s tazŇôa uca ssekkaren timessi di tendint.  
\v 20 Iryazen n ∆źay nnqeŇôben uca Šļďrin ddexxan yuŇôi …£ar ujenna zi tendint. Nitni war zemmaren ad arewŇôen …£ar da uŇôa …£ar din, \add minzi\add* Ňôgens i tu…£a yarewŇôen …£ar ŇôexŇôa, inneqŇôeb-dd \add i umen…£i\add* x wenni ten iŠłćeffaren.  
\v 21 \add Umi\add* iŠļďar Yacuwa d marra ayt n Israil belli \add inni tu…£a rajan di\add* tnuffra, ŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠fen tandint uca yuŇôi ddexxan zi tendint, …õeqben-dd nitni uca wtin iryazen n ∆źay.  
\v 22 Inni dd-iff…£en zi tendint, ruŠł•en i umsagar akidsen, aŇôami \add iryazen n ∆źay\add* dewŇôen di ŇôwesŠĻ≠ n Israiliyyen, ina …£ar u…£ezdis-a d ina …£ar u…£ezdis nne…£ni, uca nitni …£eŇôben xasen aŇôami war zzaysen iqqim uŇôa d ijjen ad yarweŇô ni…£ ad injem. \x ‚óė \xo 8:22 \xt A…õwd. 7:2\x*  
\v 23 Men…õen aje«ßid n ∆źay am iddar \add …õad\add* u iwyen t …£ar Yacuwa.   
\m
