\v 26 Yacuwa war issehwi afus nnes i isswiŠļďŠļďŠłćen s uŠł•ric aŇôami tu…£a iŠł•arrem marra imezda…£ n ∆źay \add i uteŠł•Šł•i\add*.  
\v 27 Ksin Israiliyyen m…£ir Ňôebhayem d tkeccaŠłćt n tendint nni i yixef nsen …õlaŠł•sab awaŇô n SIDI, \add awaŇô\add* nni yumur Netta i Yacuwa. \x ‚óė \xo 8:27 \xt ŇėxŇô. 31:22, 26; Yac. 8:2\x*  
