\m  
\s1 A…õaltar x wedrar n Ibal d t…£uri n Ccari…õa  
\m
\v 30 \add Xenni\add* ibna Yacuwa ijj n u…õalŠĻ≠ar i SIDI, AREBBI n Israil, x wedrar n ∆źibal,  
