\c 9
\s1 TaŠł•raymect n ayt n Jib…õun  
\m
\v 1 Umi marra ije«ßiden, inni ye«ßan x ujemmaŠłć n L‚ÄôUrdun ŠĻ£rin x man aya - \add ije«ßiden\add* x Temmurt n Idurar, di Temmurt IwaŠĻ≠an u …£ar marra tma n ŇėebŠł•ar Ameqqran aŇô qibańć i \add idurar n\add* Lubnan: IŠł•ittiyyen d Imuriyyen d ayt n Ken…õan d Ifariziyyen d IŠł•iwiyyen d Iyabusiyyen -\f ‚óľ \fr 9:1 \ft \+fk ŇėebŠł•ar Ameqqran\ft  - ni…£ ‚ÄėIll Ameqqran‚Äô. ŇėebŠł•ar-a qqaren as di Arif ‚ÄėŇėebŠł•ar AmeŠļďyan‚Äô u isem nnes d jdid aqa-t ‚ÄėIll Agrakal‚Äô.\f*  
\v 2 munen nitni Šł•ima ad mmen…£en ak-d Yacuwa u ak-d Israil x ijj n array.  
\v 3 \add Umi\add* imezda…£ n Jib…õun sŇôin min tu…£a igga Yacuwa ak-d AriŠł•a d ∆źay,  
\v 4 ggin t s teŠł•raymect. Nitni uyuren deg webrid uca ggin ixef nsen d imsekkan. Iwyen tixuncay tibuŇôay x i…£yaŇô nsen, tixuncay n yiŇôem tibuŇôay ttwacarrgent u twaxeyyŠłćent \add …õawed\add* i binu.  
\v 5 \add Qqnen …õawed\add* tisiŇôa d Ňôbari, ittwaŠłćarrfen x iŠłćaren nsen u yarŠłćen arruŠłć abuŇôay, u marra a…£rum n Ňôe…õweńć nsen tu…£a yuŠļďe…£ ittfruruy.   
\m
\v 6 Uyuren \add ammu\add* …£ar Yacuwa di ŇômargeŠł• n Ňô…õeskar n Jiljal, nnan as i netta u i ayt n Israil: ‚ÄúNeccin nusa-dd zeg ict n temmurt tigg ∑ej. Ňėexxu xenni, ggem ijj n Ňô…õahd akidne…£.‚ÄĚ  
\v 7 Arrin-dd iryazen n Israil x IŠł•iwiyyen: ‚ÄúAd ta…£ kenniw tzedd…£em jar ane…£. Mammec nzemmar ad kidwem negg ijj n Ňô…õahd?‚ÄĚ  
\v 8 Nitni maca nnan i Yacuwa: ‚ÄúNeccin d imsexxaren nnec.‚ÄĚ \add Xenni\add* inna asen Yacuwa: ‚ÄúMin te…õnam kenniw d manis i dd-tusim?‚ÄĚ  
\v 9 Nitni arrin-dd xas: ‚ÄúImsexxaren nnec usin-dd zeg ict n temmurt tigg ∑ej aŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠as di ŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠we…õ n Yisem n SIDI, AREBBI nwem. Minzi neccin nesŇôa xas Ňôexbar u x marra min igga di MiŠĻ£ra,  
\v 10 d marra min igga Netta ak-d ije«ßiden n ayt n Imuriyyen inni ye«ßan a…£irin i L‚ÄôUrdun, SiŠł•un, aje«ßid n Šł§acbun, d ∆źuj, aje«ßid n Bacan nni tu…£a izedde…£ di ∆źactarut. \x ‚óė \xo 9:10 \xt ŇėxŇô. 21:24, 33; A…õwd. 1:4\x*  
\v 11 Uca ssiwŇôen akidne…£ im…£aren nne…£ d marra imezda…£ n temmurt, nnan: ‚ÄėŠĻ¨ŠĻ≠fem Ňôe…õweńć deg ufus nwem i webrid, uyurem i umsagar akidsen uca ad asen tinim: Neccin d imsexxaren nwem.‚Äô Xenni Ňôexxu, ggem akidne…£ ijj n Ňô…õahd.  
\v 12 A…£rum-a nne…£ da tu…£a …õad iŠł•ma umi t-i-dd akidne…£ neksi zi tudrin nne…£ d Ňôe…õweńć deg wass aŇôami …£arwem dd-neŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠ef abrid. Ňėexxu aqa-t yuŠļďe…£ idweŇô ittfruruy.  
\v 13 UŇôa d tixuncay n yiŇôem n binu nni neccur, tu…£a atent n jdid, maca xzarem, Ňôexxu fe«ßqent. Aqa \add d\add* arruŠłć nne…£ d sandaliyat nne…£ Šł•fant s webrid i igg ∑ejen s waŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠as.‚ÄĚ  
\v 14 \add Xenni\add* ksin iryazen n Israil zi Ňôe…õweńć. War ksin ccwar zeg uqemmum n SIDI.  
\v 15 Igga Yacuwa akidsen Ňôehna u igga akidsen \add …õawed\add* ijj n Ňô…õahd, ad ten yejj ad ddaren uca uŇôa d ŇôŠł•ukkam n tmesmunt jju«ßen asen.   
