\v 16 Awarni tŇôata n wussan awarni i umi tu…£a i d asen wcin Ňô…õahd, sŇôan nitni belli aqa d jjiran nsen, u aqa zedd…£en di ŇôwesŠĻ≠ nsen.  
\v 17 \add Minzi\add* ayt n Israil kksen \add iqiŠłćan nsen\add* uca iwŠłćen …£ar tneddam nsen deg wass wiss tŇôata. Tu…£a tineddam nsen Jib…õun d Kafira d Bi…õrut d Qaryat-Ya…õarim.  
