\v 19 \add Xenni\add* nnan marra ŇôŠł•ukkam n tmesmunt: ‚ÄúNeccin nejju«ß asen \add aya\add* …£ar SIDI, AREBBI n Israil. S uyenni Ňôexxu war nzemmar ad ten nŠł•ada.  
\v 20 IttxeŠĻ£ŠĻ£a ad nkemmeŇô \add taja«ßit-a\add* u ad ten nejj ad ddaren, maŠł•end war xane…£ dd-iweŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠i uduqqez n we…£Šłćab di ssibbet n tja«ßit nni d asen negga.  
\v 21 ŇėŠł•ukkam nnan asen: ‚ÄúNitni ad qqimen ddaren uca ad dewŇôen d inezdamen d inuyam i marra tamesmunt, am mammec d asen t nnan ŇôŠł•ukkam.‚ÄĚ   
\m
\v 22 IŇôa…£a i-ten Yacuwa, inna: ‚ÄúMayemmi xane…£ tcemtem, tennam: ‚ÄėNeccin nzedde…£ …£ar Ňôagg ∑aj s waŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠as xawem!‚Äô, waxxa kenniw tzedd…£em di¬†Ňôwest n temmurt nne…£?  
\v 23 Ňėexxu xenni, kenniw tŠĶČttwane…õŇôem. War zzaywem ittwakkes ad tiŇôim d imsexxaren, inezdamen d inuyam i Taddart n AREBBI inu.‚ÄĚ \f ‚óľ \fr 9:23 \ft \+fk War zzaywem ittwakkes ad tiŇôim ....\ft  - s T…õibranit ‚ÄėWar zzaywem ittwaqeŠĻ£ŠĻ£ ...‚Äô.\f*  
\v 24 Nitni arrin-dd x Yacuwa, nnan: ‚ÄúI imsexxaren nnec ittwanna nican belli SIDI, AREBBI nwem, yumur amsexxar nnes Musa, aqa Netta ad awem iwca marra tammurt uca ad ihellek marra imezda…£ n temmurt zzat i tiŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠awin nwem. \add S uya\add* tu…£a negg ∑ed aŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠as x tudart nne…£ zzat i wudem nwem. S uyenni i negga neccin aya. \f ‚óľ \fr 9:24 \ft \+fk x tudart nne…£\ft  - s T…õibranit ‚Äėx Ňôe…õmur nne…£‚Äô.\f*¬†¬†\x ‚óė \xo 9:24 \xt A…õwd. 7:1, 2\x*  
\v 25 Ňėexxu \add xenni\add*, xzar, aqa ane…£ deg ufus nnec. Egg akidne…£ min tŠĶČttwaŇôid mliŠł• d min i«ßan nican di tiŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠awin nnec Šł•ima ad zzayne…£ tegged.‚ÄĚ  
\v 26 Ammu i zzaysen igga uca netta ifekk i-ten zeg ufus n ayt n Israil, aŇôami nitni war ten n…£in ca.  
