\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 10
\s1 Amen…£i …£ar Jib…õun  
\m
\v 1 Imsar, umi Aduni-ŠĻĘadaq, aje«ßid n Urcalim isŇôa, aqa Yacuwa tu…£a iŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠ef ∆źay, iŠł•arrem i-tt qa…õ uca aqa igga ak-d ∆źay d aje«ßid nnes am tu…£a igga ak-d AriŠł•a u ak-d uje«ßid nnes u aqa imezda…£ n Jib…õun ggin Ňôehna ak-d ayt n Israil u zedd…£en di ŇôwesŠĻ≠ nsen, \x ‚óė \xo 10:1 \xt Yac. 6:15; 9:15\x*  
\v 2 \add aqa\add* nitni gg ∑eden aŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠as, minzi Jib…õun tu…£a d ict n tendint tem…£ar, umi tt tu…£a am yicten zi \add jar\add* tneddam n tgeldit. Tu…£a-tt tem…£ar x ∆źay u marra iryazen nnes tu…£a aten d ayt n bu-te…£ruŠłćt.  
\v 3 Issekk Aduni-Zedek, aje«ßid n Urcalim, \add imsekkan\add* …£ar Huham, aje«ßid n Šł§abrun, …£ar Fir‚Äôam, aje«ßid n Yarmut, …£ar Yafi…õ, aje«ßid n Laxic u …£ar Dabir, aje«ßid n ∆źajlun, inna:  
\v 4 ‚ÄúGe…õ…õdem-dd …£ari u tewcem ayi afus. Ejj ane…£ ad newwet Jib…õun, minzi tegga Ňôehna ak-d Yacuwa u ak-d ayt n Israil.‚ÄĚ  
\v 5 Nitni munen uca ge…õ…õden xemsa n ije«ßiden n Imuriyyen: aje«ßid n Urcalim, aje«ßid n Šł§abrun, aje«ßid n Yarmut, aje«ßid n ∆źajlun, nitni d marra Ňô…õeskar nsen uca nnŠłćen i Jib…õun uca kkaren mmen…£en akides.   
\m
\v 6 Ssekken iryazen n Jib…õun \add ireqqasen\add* i Yacuwa, …£ar ŇômargeŠł• n Ňô…õeskar di Jiljal, nnan: ‚ÄúWar semmeŠł• ifassen nnec deg imsexxaren nnec, as-dd de…£ya …£arne…£. Senjem ane…£ d tewced ane…£ afus, minzi marra ije«ßiden n ayt n Imuriyyen, inni i izedd…£en deg idurar, aqa munen xane…£.‚ÄĚ   
\m
\v 7 \add Xenni\add* ige…õ…õed-dd Yacuwa zi Jiljal, netta d marra Ňôgens n Ňô…õeskar akides d marra ayt n bu-te…£ruŠłćt imeŠł•Šłćen.  
\v 8 \add Minzi\add* SIDI inna i Yacuwa ‚ÄúWar ttegg ∑ed ca zzaysen, minzi wci…£ ten deg ufus nnec. UŇôa d ijj zzaysen war izemmar ad ibedd zzat i wudem nnec.‚ÄĚ  
\v 9 Yacuwa ihwa-dd xasen s Ňô…£efŇôet. Ige…õ…õaden-dd zi Jiljal «ßiŇôet am tekmeŇô.  
\v 10 SIDI issnexŇôe…õ i-ten zzat i wudem n Israil uca igga asen ijj n we…£Šłćar d ameqqran …£ar Jib…õun uca netta iŠłćfar i-ten x webrid ittge…õ…õaden …£ar Bayt-Šł§urun uca iwwet i-ten aŇô ŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠arf n ∆źaziqqa d Maqida.  
\v 11 Imsar umi nitni arewŇôen zzat i wudem n Israil deg uhekkwu …£ar Bayt-Šł§urun, aqa SIDI inŠłćar xasen iŠļďra d imeqqranen zeg ujenna aŇô ∆źaziqqa uca mmuten. Inni immuten s ibquqen n tebruri tu…£a aten ktar zeg inni ittwan…£en s ssif s ifassen n ayt n Israil.   
\m
\v 12 Xenni issiweŇô Yacuwa ak-d SIDI, deg wass umi isellem SIDI Imuriyyen i ayt n Israil, inna zzat i tiŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠awin n Israiliyyen: ‚Äú\add A\add* tafuct, bedd …£ar Jib…õun, i \add cek a,\add* ayur, …£ar te…£zurt n Ayalun‚ÄĚ  
\v 13 Uca tafuct tbedd d uyur iqqim ibedd aŇôami yu…£a Ňôgens tas…£art x Ňô…õedyan nnes. Ma war yura man aya deg wedlis ittwannŠłćen n umsegged? Tafuct tbedd di ŇôwesŠĻ≠ n ujenna u war tqe«ßeq ad t…£e«ßi, …õŇôayen ijj n wass ikmeŇô.  
\v 14 War din i«ßi uŇôa d ijj n wass am wanita, \add war imsar\add* zic uŇôa awarni as, ijj n wass i di tu…£a isŇôa SIDI …£ar tmijja n ijj n weryaz ammu, minzi SIDI tu…£a immne…£ di ŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠we…õ n Israil.  
\v 15 \add Xenni\add* i…õqeb-dd Yacuwa d marra Israil akides, …£ar ŇômargeŠł• n Ňô…õeskar di Jiljal.   
\b  
\m
\v 16 Xemsa n ije«ßiden nni arewŇôen uca nnufaren deg ifri …£ar Maqqida.  
