\v 18 \add Xenni\add* inna Yacuwa: ‚ÄúSeqnunniyem tiŠĻ£uŠłćar d timeqqranin x uqemmum n ifri uca ssbeddem iryazen xasen, Šł•ima ad xasen …õessen.  
\v 19 Kenniw \add s yixef nwem\add*, war tŠĶČtt…£imam tbeddem. ŠłĆfarem Ňô…õedyan nwem, wtem a…£ezdis aneggaru nsen. War ten ttejjim ad adfen …£ar tneddam nsen, minzi SIDI, AREBBI nwem, igga awem ten deg ufus nwem.‚ÄĚ  
\v 20 Umi ikemmeŇô i-ten Yacuwa d ayt n Israil s ict n tecti tameqqrant aŇôami ttwaqŠłćan nitni, uca iwŠłćen \add m…£ir\add* inni yarewŇôen …£ar tneddam ifaryen,  
\v 21 aqa yaregg ∑eŠł• marra Ňôgens di Ňôehna …£ar Yacuwa di ŇômargeŠł• n Ňô…õeskar …£ar Maqqida. UŇôa d ijj \add war iz…õim\add* ad issenhez iŇôes nnes x ayt n Israil.   
\m
