\v 23 Nitni ggin \add t\add* ammu, ssuff…£en-dd xemsa n ije«ßiden zeg ifri …£ares: aje«ßid n Urcalim, aje«ßid n Šł§abrun, aje«ßid n Yarmut, aje«ßid n Laxic d uje«ßid n ∆źajlun.  
\v 24 Umi dd-ssuff…£en nitni ije«ßiden nni …£ar Yacuwa, iŇôa…£a Yacuwa marra iryazen n Israil uca inna i ikumandaren x i…õeskariyyen nni tu…£a akides iruŠł•en: ‚ÄúQarrbem-dd uca sarsem iŠłćaren nwem x tmejjarin n ije«ßiden-a.‚ÄĚ Qarrben-dd nitni uca ssarsen iŠłćaren x timejjarin nsen.  
\v 25 \add Xenni\add* inna asen Yacuwa: ‚ÄúWar ttegg ∑dem ca, war ttejjim ad i…õqez wuŇô nwem, iŇôim d iryazen u iŇôim tmeŠł•Šłćem, minzi ammu i …£a igg SIDI ak-d marra Ňô…õedyan nwem, inni ak-d tŠĶČttmen…£am.‚ÄĚ  
\v 26 Xenni iwwet i-ten Yacuwa uca in…£a i-ten. YayeŇô i-ten …£ar xemsa n tŠł•enya uca qqimen ayŇôen …£ar tŠł•enya aŇôami d tameddit. \x ‚óė \xo 10:26 \xt A…õwd. 21:23; Yac. 8:29\x*  
\v 27 Imsar …£ar Ňôweqt n u…£e«ßay n tfuct, issekk Yacuwa maŠł•end ad ten-i-dd-kksen zi tŠł•enya, ad ten nŠłćaren deg ifri i di tu…£a nnuffaren. Xenni ggin tiŠĻ£uŠłćar d timeqqranin x uqemmum n ifri, \add inni din i«ßan\add* aŇô ass-a.  
\v 28 Deg wass nni iŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠ef Yacuwa \bd Maqqida\bd* uca iwwet i-tt s ŇôeqŠłće…õ n ssif. Uca aje«ßid nnes, iŠł•arrem i-t uŇôa d \add marra\add* nitni d kuŇô Ňôe…õmar nni \add i«ßan\add* deg wemcan nni. War ijji ad iqqim uŇôa d ijj n umarweŇô uca igga ak-d uje«ßid n Maqqida am mammec tu…£a igga ak-d uje«ßid n AriŠł•a.  
\v 29 \add Xenni\add* iŠļďwa Yacuwa ak-d marra ayt n Israil zi Maqqida …£ar Libna uca immne…£ ak-d Libna.  
\v 30 Uca SIDI iwca i-tt deg ufus n Israil, ak-d uje«ßid nnes. Iwwet i-tt s ŇôeqŠłće…õ n ssif ak-d marra Ňôe…õmar i dayes \add i«ßan\add*, war ijji ad iqqim uŇôa d ijj n umarweŇô, uca igga ak-d uje«ßid nnes am mammec tu…£a igga ak-d uje«ßid n AriŠł•a.   
\m
\v 31 \add Xenni\add* iŠļďwa Yacuwa zi Libna …£ar \bd Laxic\bd* d marra Israil akides uca inneŠłć as-dd i tendint uca immne…£ akides.  
\v 32 SIDI iwca Laxic deg ufus n Israil. Uca Israil iŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠ef i-tt deg wass wiss tnayen uca iwwet i-tt s ŇôeqŠłće…õ n ssif ak-d marra Ňôe…õmar i dayes \add i«ßan\add*, ammu nican am mammec tu…£a i-tt igga ak-d Libna.  
\v 33 Xenni ige…õ…õed Huram, aje«ßid n Jazar, maŠł•end ad i…õawen Laxic, \add maca\add* Yacuwa iwwet i-t uŇôa d Ňôgens nnes aŇôami war ijji ad …£ares iqqim uŇôa d ijj n umarweŇô.   
\m
\v 34 Yacuwa iŠļďwa zi Laxic …£ar \bd ∆źajlun\bd* d marra Israil akides uca nnŠłćen as-dd uca mmen…£en akides.  
\v 35 ŠĻ¨ŠĻ≠fen tt deg wass nni uca wtin tt s ŇôeqŠłće…õ n ssif uca deg wass nni iŠł•arrem marra Ňôe…õmar i dayes \add i«ßan\add*, ammu nican am mammec tu…£a igga ak-d Laxic.   
\m
\v 36 IŠļďwa Yacuwa zi¬†∆źajlun …£ar \bd Šł§abrun\bd* d marra Israil akides, uca mmen…£en akides.  
\v 37 Nitni ŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠fen tt uca wtin tt s ŇôeqŠłće…õ n ssif, aje«ßid nnes d marra tineddam nnes ak-d marra Ňôe…õmar i dayes \add i«ßan\add*. War ijji ad iqqim uŇôa d ijj n umarweŇô, ammu nican am mammec tu…£a igga ak-d ∆źajlun. Netta iŠł•arrem i-tt ak-d marra Ňôe…õmar i dayes \add i«ßan\add*.   
\m
\v 38 Uca idweŇô-dd Yacuwa …£ar \bd Dabir\bd* d marra Israil akides uca immne…£ akides.  
\v 39 Netta iŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠ef i-tt u nitni wtin aje«ßid nnes d marra tineddam nnes s ŇôeqŠłće…õ n ssif uca Šł•arrmen marra Ňôe…õmar i dayes \add i«ßan\add*. Netta war ijji ad iqqim uŇôa d ijj n umarweŇô. Am mammec tu…£a igga netta ak-d Šł§abrun, ammu igga \add …õawed\add* ak-d Dabir u ak-d uje«ßid nnes igga am tu…£a igga ak-d uje«ßid n Libna.  
\v 40 \add Ammu\add* i i…£Ňôeb Yacuwa x marra tammurt: Tammurt n Idurar d \add Temmurt n\add* Ljanub d Temmurt IwaŠĻ≠an, d marra ije«ßiden nsen. War ijji ad iqqim uŇôa d ijj n umarweŇô. Marra min tu…£a ittarran nnefs, iŠł•arrem i-t i uteŠł•Šł•i, am mammec tu…£a i d as yumur SIDI AREBBI n Israil. \x ‚óė \xo 10:40 \xt A…õwd. 7:2; 20:16, 17; Yac. 8:2\x*  
\v 41 Yacuwa iwwet i-ten zi Qadac-Barni…õ aŇô ∆Ēazza u ammu uŇôa d marra tammurt n Jucan, aŇô Jib…õun.  
\v 42 IŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠ef Yacuwa ije«ßiden-a d temmurt nsen s ict n tecti, minzi SIDI, AREBBI n Israil, immne…£ di ŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠we…õ n Israil.  
\v 43 \add Xenni\add* i…õqeb Yacuwa …£ar ŇômargeŠł• n Ňô…õeskar di Jiljal d marra Israil akides.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 11
\s1 Amen…£i Šłćidd i uje«ßid Yabin d ije«ßiden nni akis i«ßan  
\m
\v 1 Umi Yabin, aje«ßid n \bd Šł§aŠĻ£ur\bd*, isŇôa aya, issekk …£ar Yubab, aje«ßid n \bd Madun\bd*, …£ar uje«ßid n \bd Cimrun\bd*, …£ar uje«ßid n \bd Akcaf\bd*,  
\v 2 u …£ar ije«ßiden inni tu…£a \add izedd…£en\add* …£ar ccamal di Temmurt n Idurar u di ŇėewŠłća …£ar ljanub zi Kinnarut u di Temmurt IwaŠĻ≠an u x tiwririn n Dur …£ar Ňô…£arb,  
\v 3 …£ar ayt n Ken…õan di ccarq d Ňô…£arb, Imuriyyen, IŠł•ittiyyen, Ifiriziyyen, Iyabusiyyen deg idurar d IŠł•iwiyyen …£ar uŠłćar n \add wedrar\add* n Hirmun, di temmurt n MiŠĻ£fa.  
\v 4 Ff…£en-dd nitni s marra Ňô…õeskar nsen akidsen, ijj n ubarra ameqqran n Ňôgens, am yijdi …£ar tma n ŇôebŠł•ar, anect aŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠as, uca \add arni …£ares\add* aŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠as s waŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠as n iysan d ikarruten.  
\v 5 Marra ije«ßiden-a Ňôa…£an-dd xasen uca usin-dd, wtin iqiŠłćan nsen jmi…õ …£ar waman n Mayrum i umen…£i Šłćidd i Israil.*   
\b  
\m
\v 6 Inna SIDI i Yacuwa: ‚ÄúWar zzaysen ttegg ∑ed, minzi tiwecca …£ar Ňôweqt ammu Ňôexxu ad ten gge…£ ttwa…£eŇôben marra zzat i wudem n Israil. Cek ad tqessed iŠļďewran n iŠłćaren n iysan nsen uca ad tesscemŠłćed ikarruten nsen di tmessi.‚ÄĚ   
\m
\v 7 Yacuwa s marra Ňô…õeskar akides, iffe…£-dd …£arsen s ict n Ňô…£efŇôet …£ar waman n Mayrum uca wŠłćan-dd xasen.  
\v 8 SIDI igga i-ten deg ufus n Israil uca nitni wtin ten, Šłćfaren ten aŇô ŠĻĘidun-Ameqqran d Misrafut-Mayim, u aŇô taysart n MiŠĻ£fa …£ar ccarq. Nitni qŠłćan ten aŇôami war zzaysen jjin ad iqqim uŇôa d ijj n umarweŇô.  
\v 9 Yacuwa igga akidsen am mammec d as inna SIDI. Netta iqess iŠļďewran n iŠłćaren n iysan nsen uca issecmeŠłć ikarruten nsen s tmessi.   
\m
\v 10 Di Ňôweqt nni i…õqeb Yacuwa uca iŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠ef Šł§aŠĻ£ur uca iwta aje«ßid nnes s \add ŇôeqŠłće…õ n\add* ssif, minzi Šł§aŠĻ£ur tu…£a-t qbeŇô d aze«ßif x marra tigeldiwin-a.  
\v 11 Wtin marra Ňôe…õmar \add iddaren\add* nni dayes i«ßan s ŇôeqŠłće…õ n ssif uca Šł•arrmen ten u n…£in ten. War iqqim walu zi marra min ittarran nnefs uca issecmeŠłć Šł§aŠĻ£ur s tmessi.  
\v 12 IŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠ef Yacuwa marra tineddam n ije«ßiden-a s marra ije«ßiden nsen uca iwta i-ten s ŇôeqŠłće…õ n ssif uca iŠł•arrem i-ten, am mammec tu…£a yumur Musa, amsexxar n SIDI. \x ‚óė \xo 11:12 \xt A…õwd. 20:16, 17; Yac. 10:40\x*  
\v 13 Marra tineddam nni ibedden x tiwririn war tent sscemŠłćen Israiliyyen s tmessi, m…£ir Šł§aŠĻ£ur umi issecmeŠłć Yacuwa s tmessi.  
\v 14 KeccŠłćen ayt n Israil marra takeccaŠłćt n tneddam d Ňôebhayem i ixef nsen. Maca nitni n…£in marra iwdan s ŇôeqŠłće…õ n ssif, aŇôami ten teŠł•Šł•an. Marra min ittaran nnefs, war zzayes jjin uŇôa d ijj.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Lista n marra min iŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠ef Yacuwa n temmurt n Ken…õan  
\m
\v 15 Am mammec \add t\add* yumur SIDI i umsexxar nnes Musa, ammu i t igga Musa x Yacuwa, uca ammu \add i-t\add* igga Yacuwa. Netta war ismiŠł• uŇôa deg ijj n wawaŇô zi marra \add awaŇôen\add* i yumur SIDI i Musa \add maŠł•end ad t igg\add*. \x ‚óė \xo 11:15 \xt Uf. 23:32, 33; 34:12; ŇėxŇô. 33:52; A…õwd. 7:2; 20:16\x*  
\v 16 \add Ammu\add* iŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠ef Yacuwa marra tammurt nni: Tammurt n Idurar d marra \add Tammurt n\add* Ljanub d marra tammurt n Jucan d Temmurt IwaŠĻ≠an d ŇėewŠłća d idurar n Israil d ŇôwaŠĻ≠a nnes,  
\v 17 \add marra tammurt\add* zeg Wedrar d Aqeccar, wenni isge…õ…õaden …£ar Sa…õir aŇô Ba…õl-Jad, di teysart n Lubnan, swadday i wedrar n Šł§irmun. Marra ije«ßiden nsen iŠł•ebbes i-ten, iwta i-ten uca in…£a i-ten.  
\v 18 AŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠as n wussan i immne…£ Yacuwa ak-d marra ije«ßiden-a.  
\v 19 War i«ßi uŇôa d ict n tendint i iggin Ňôehna ak-d ayt n Israil, m…£ir IŠł•iwiyyen, inni tu…£a izedd…£en di Jib…õun. Nitni ŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠fen tent marra s umen…£i.  
\v 20 Minzi SIDI tu…£a igga ad isseqseŠł• uŇô nsen aŇô dd …£a ff…£en ad mmen…£en ak-d Israil, Šł•ima ad ten iŠł•arrem uca war xasen yareŠł•Šł•em, Šł•ima ad ten iqŠłća, am mammec tu…£a yumur SIDI i Musa.   
\m
\v 21 Di Ňôweqt nni iffe…£ Yacuwa uca iteŠł•Šł•a \bd I…õanaqiyyen\bd* zi temmurt n idurar, zi Šł§abrun, zi Dabir, zi ∆źanab, zi marra Tammurt n Idurar n Yahuda u zi marra tammurt n idurar n Israil. Yacuwa iŠł•arrem i-ten ak-d tneddam nsen i uteŠł•Šł•i.  
\v 22 Di temmurt n ayt Israil war qqimen …õad I…õanaqiyyen. Qqimen m…£ir di ∆Ēazza, Jat d Acdud.   
\m
\v 23 IŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠ef Yacuwa marra tammurt nni, am mammec marra i tu…£a issiweŇô SIDI …£ar Musa, uca Yacuwa iwca i-tt d Ňôwart i Israil …õlaŠł•sab tirbi…õin n tqebbaŇô nsen. \add Xenni\add* tu…£a tammurt tareyyeŠł• zeg umen…£i.   
\b  
