\m  
\c 12
\s1 A…£Ňôeb x waŠł•d u tŇôatin n ije«ßiden  
\m
\v 1 Ina d ije«ßiden n temmurt, inni x …£eŇôben ayt n Israil uca \add xenni\add* ŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠fen nitni tammurt nsen d Ňôwart, a…£irin i L‚ÄôUrdun zi manis i d tneqqar tfuct, zi te…£zart n Arnun aŇô idurar n Šł§irmun d marra ŇėewŠłća di ccarq.   
\m
\v 2 ∆Ēar umezwaru nsen, SiŠł•un, aje«ßid n Imuriyyen, wenni tu…£a izedd…£en di Šł§acbun, netta iŠł•kem \add x jjwayeh\add* zi ∆źaru…õir i i«ßan …£ar tma n te…£zart n Arnun, \add aŇô\add* ŇôwesŠĻ≠ n te…£zart, u x wezyen n Jil…õad aŇô ti…£zart n Yabbuq, \add aqa-t\add* d aymir n ayt n ∆źammun,  
\v 3 u x ŇėewŠłća aŇô ŇôebŠł•ar n Kinnarut di ccarq u aŇô ŇôebŠł•ar n ŇėewŠłća, ŇėebŠł•ar Ame«ßaŠł•, di ccarq, abrid n Bayt-Yacimut, u zi ljanub aŇô swadday i teysarin n Fisja.   
\m
\v 4 \add Xenni\add* tammurt n ∆źuj, aje«ßid n Bacan, \add wenni i«ßan\add* zi¬†min iqqimen zeg Irafawiyyen, \add jwaheŇô\add* i tu…£a izedd…£en di ∆źactarut d Idra…õi. \x ‚óė \xo 12:4 \xt  A…õwd. 1:4\x*  
\v 5 Netta iŠł•kem x idurar n Šł§irmun, x Salxa u x marra Bacan aŇô weymir n Ijacuriyyen d Ima…õkiyyen u x wezyen n Jil…õad aŇô tammurt n SiŠł•un, aje«ßid n Šł§acbun.   
\m
\v 6 Musa, amsexxar n SIDI, ak-d ayt n Israil, wtin ten u Musa, amsexxar n SIDI, tu…£a iwca \add tammurt nni\add* d Ňôwart i Irubiniyyen d Ijadiyyen u i wezyen n teqbińć n Manassa. \x ‚óė \xo 12:6 \xt ŇėxŇô. 21:24; 32:33\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 7 Ina d ije«ßiden n temmurt inni x i…£Ňôeb Yacuwa d ayt n Israil, …£ar ujemmaŠłć n L‚ÄôUrdun di l…£arb, zi Ba…õl-Jad di teysart n Lubnan aŇô adrar aqeccar wenni issge…õ…õden …£ar Sa…õir. Uca Yacuwa iwca i-tt d Ňôwart i tqebbaŇô n Israil …õlaŠł•sab tirbi…õin nsen, \x ‚óė \xo 12:7 \xt Yac. 10:40\x*  
\v 8 Di Temmurt n Idurar u di Temmurt IwaŠĻ≠an u di ŇėewŠłća u di teysarin u di ŇôexŇôa u di \add Temmurt n\add* Ljanub: IŠł•ittiyyen, Imuriyyen, ayt n Ken…õan, Ifariziyyen, IŠł•iwiyyen d Iyabusiyyen.   
