\c 13
\s1 SIDI issiweŇô ak-d Yacuwa  
\m
\v 1 Umi tu…£a Yacuwa d awessar uca im…£ar deg wussan \add n tudart nnes\add*, inna as SIDI: ‚ÄúCek tewsared u tem…£ared deg wussan uca \add …õad\add* teqqim aŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠as n temmurt maŠł•end ad tt teksid d Ňôwart.  
\v 2 Ta d tammurt iqqimen: marra iduwwaren n IfilisŠĻ≠iniyyen u marra \add jjwayeh n\add* Ijacuriyyen,  
\v 3 zeg \add ye…£zar n\add* CiŠł•ur nni \add issizzŇôen\add* zzat i wudem n MiŠĻ£ra, aŇô aymir n ∆źiqrun di ccamal nni ittwaŠł•seb-dd \add d tammurt\add* n ayt n Ken…õan, \add dayes\add* xemsa n Ňôbacat \add n tneddam\add* n IfilisŠĻ≠iniyyen, \add ixs ad yini\add* A…£azi d Acdudi d Acqaluni, Ajitti, d A…õaqruni, d I…õawiyyen,  
\v 4 \add uca xenni\add* zi ljanub marra tammurt n ayt n Ken…õan d Mu…£ara tenni n IŠĻ£iduniyyen, aŇô Afiq u aŇô weymir n Imuriyyen,  
\v 5 uca \add xenni\add* tammurt n Ijibliyyen d marra Lubnan manis i dd-tneqqar tfuct, zi Ba…õl-Jad swadday i wedrar n Šł§irmun aŇô mani ittakkwaŠłć \add bnadem\add* …£ar Šł§amat,  
\v 6 marra inni izedd…£en \add di jjwayeh\add* zeg idurar n Lubnan aŇô Misrafut-Mayim, marra IŠĻ£iduniyyen. Necc ad xasen aŠļďŠļďŇôe…£ zzat i wudem n ayt n Israil. Egg \add maca\add* tammurt d Ňôwart i Israil waha, am mammec d ac umure…£.‚ÄĚ   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Tas…£art n Rubin, n Jad u i wezyen n teqbińć n Manassi  
\m
\v 7 ‚ÄúBŠłća Ňôexxu tammurt-a d Ňôwart jar tes…õa n tqebbaŇô d wezyen n teqbińć n Manassa,  
\v 8 \add iryazen n Manassa\add* nni iksin ak-d Irubiniyyen d Ijadiyyen tas…£art n Ňôwart nsen nni i d asen iwca Musa x ujemmaŠłć n L‚ÄôUrdun di ccarq, am mammec d asen \add tt\add* iwca Musa, amsexxar n SIDI:  
\v 9 zi Aru…õir \add i i«ßan\add* x tma n Arnun d tendint i i«ßan di ŇôwesŠĻ≠ n te…£zurt d marra ŇôwaŠĻ≠a \add yu…õŇôan\add* zi Miydaba aŇô Dibun, \x ‚óė \xo 13:9 \xt A…õwd. 2:36\x*  
\v 10 d marra tineddam n SiŠł•un, aje«ßid n Imuriyyen wenni tu…£a iŠł•ekkmen di Šł§acbun, aŇô aymir n ayt n ∆źammun  
\v 11 uŇôa d Jil…õad d temmurt n Ijacuriyyen d Ima…õkiyyen d qa…õ wedrar n Šł§irmun d marra Bacan aŇô Salxa,  
\v 12 marra tageldit n ∆źuj, di Bacan, wenni tu…£a iŠł•ekkmen di ∆źactarut d Idra…õi. Netta tu…£a iqqim zi min iqqimen n Irafawiyyen nni tu…£a iwta i-ten Musa uca yuŠļďŠļďeŇô xasen \add zi tes…£art nsen\add*.  
\v 13 \add Maca\add* ayt n Israil war uŠļďŠļďŇôen x ayt n Ijacuriyyen d Ima…õkiyyen \add zi tes…£art nsen\add*. Jacur d Ma…õkat qqimen zedd…£en di ŇôwesŠĻ≠ n ayt n Israil aŇô ass-a.   
\m
\v 14 I teqbińć n Lawi waha umi i war iwci tas…£art. Ti…£arŠĻ£a n tmessi n SIDI, AREBBI n Israil, d tas…£art nnes, am mammec tu…£a i d as issiweŇô Netta.   
\b  
\m
\v 15 Iwca Musa i \bd teqbińć n ayt n Rubin\bd* \add tas…£art nsen\add*, …õlaŠł•sab Ňôa«ßat nsen.  
\v 16 I nitni umi dd-tekkar temmurt n Aru…õir, tenni i i«ßan …£ar tma n te…£zart n Arnun ak-d tendint nni \add i«ßan\add* di ŇôwesŠĻ≠ n te…£zurt d marra ŇôwaŠĻ≠a \add yu…õŇôan\add* aŇô Midiba.  
\v 17 Šł§acbun d marra tineddam nnes nni \add i«ßan\add* x ŇôwaŠĻ≠a \add yu…õŇôan\add*: Dibun, Bamut-Ba…õl d Bayt-Ba…õl-Ma…õun  
\v 18 d YahŠĻ£a d Qadimut d Mayfa…õa  
\v 19 d Qaryatayim d Sibma d ŠĻĘarat-Ha-CaŠł•ar x wedrar n ŇôewŠłća n te…£zurt, \f ‚óľ \fr 13:19 \ft \+fk Qiryatayim\ft  - ixs ad yini ‚Äėtnayen n tneddam‚Äô.\f*  
\v 20 d Bayt-Fa…£ur d tisawnin n Fisja d Bayt-Yacimut,  
\v 21 marra tineddam x ŇôwaŠĻ≠a \add yu…õŇôan\add* d marra tageldit n SiŠł•un, aje«ßid n Imuriyyen, inni i tu…£a iŠł•ekkmen di Šł§acbun, i x i…£Ňôeb Musa, \add am i…£Ňôeb\add* uŇôa x ŇôŠł•ukkam n Midyan: Awi d Raqam d ŠĻĘur d Šł§ur d Raba…õ, inni i d asen iwca ŠĻĘihun jjehd akides, imezda…£ n temmurt.  
\v 22 Sennej i marra inni ittwan…£en di garra, n…£in ayt n Israil …õawed Bal…õam, mmis n Ba…õur, agezzan, s ŇôeqŠłće…õ n ssif. \x ‚óė \xo 13:22 \xt ŇėxŇô. 31:8\x*  
\v 23 Tu…£a L‚ÄôUrdun ak-d jjwayeh nnes d aymir n ayt n Rubin ak-d temmurt …£ar tma nnes. Ta d tas…£art n ayt n Rubin …õlaŠł•sab Ňôa«ßat nsen, ak-d tneddam d dcurat nsen. \x ‚óė \xo 13:23 \xt ŇėxŇô. 34:14, 15\x*   
\m
\v 24 Iwca Musa i \bd teqbińć n Jad\bd*, i ayt n Jad, \add tas…£art nsen\add* …õlaŠł•sab Ňôa«ßat nsen.  
\v 25 I nitni umi dd-tekkar temmurt n Ya…õazir d marra tineddam n Jil…õad d wezyen n temmurt n ayt n ∆źammun aŇô Aru…õir nni \add i«ßan\add* zzat i wudem n Rabba,  
\v 26 zi Šł§acbun aŇô Ramat-MiŠĻ£fa d BuŠĻ≠unim, u zi MaŠł•anayim aŇô aymir n Dabir.  
\v 27 U di ŇôewŠłća n te…£zurt: Bayt-Haram d Bayt-Nimra d Sukkut d ŠĻĘafun d min iqqimen n tgeldit n SiŠł•un, aje«ßid n Šł§acbun, L‚ÄôUrdun d jjwayeh nnes aŇô aneggar n¬†ŇôebŠł•ar n Kinnarat x ujemmaŠłć n L‚ÄôUrdun …£ar ccarq.  
\v 28 Ta d tas…£art n ayt n Jad, …õlaŠł•sab Ňôa«ßat nsen, tineddam d dcurat nnes.   
\m
\v 29 Iwca Musa i \bd wezyen n teqbińć n Manassa\bd* \add tas…£art nsen\add*. Tekkar as-dd i wezyen n teqbińć n Manassa, …õlaŠł•sab Ňôa«ßat nsen.  
\v 30 Tu…£a tammurt nsen zi MaŠł•anayim: marra Bacan, marra tageldit n ∆źuj, aje«ßid n Bacan, d marra dcurat n Ya‚Äôir nni \add i«ßan\add* di Bacan, settin n tneddam. \x ‚óė \xo 13:30 \xt ŇėxŇô. 32:14, A…õwd. 3:4, 14\x*  
\v 31 D wezyen n Jil…õad d ∆źactarut d Idri…õi, tineddam n tgeldit n ∆źuj di Bacan, kkaren-dd i iŠł•enjiren n Maxir, mmis n Manassa, aqa i wezyen n iŠł•enjiren n Maxir, …õlaŠł•sab Ňôa«ßat nsen.  
\v 32 Tina d \add jjwayeh\add* i tu…£a ibŠłća Musa d Ňôwart di ŇôewŠłćat n Mu‚Äôab, x ujemmaŠłć n L‚ÄôUrdun, …£ar AriŠł•a, …£ar ccarq.   
\m
\v 33 Maca i \bd teqbińć n Lawi\bd* war d as iwci Musa ca tas…£art. SIDI, AREBBI n Israil d tas…£art nsen, am mammec tu…£a akidsen issiweŇô. \x ‚óė \xo 13:33 \xt ŇėxŇô. 18:20; A…õwd. 10:9; 18:2\x*¬†¬†*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 14
\s1 AbeŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠u n temmurt …£ar ujemmaŠłć n ye…£zar n L‚ÄôUrdun  
\m
\v 1 Tina d tseqqar i ŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠fen ayt n Israil di temmurt n Ken…õan, tinni i d asen ibŠłća \add d Ňôwart\add* ukehhan Ali…õazar d Yacuwa, mmis n Nun, d ize«ßifen \add n tudrin\add* n ibabaten n tqebbaŇô n ayt n Israil. \x ‚óė \xo 14:1 \xt ŇėxŇô. 34:17\x*  
\v 2 S tqedduŠł•t \add ŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠fen\add* marra tas…£art nsen, am mammec \add t\add* yumur SIDI s tsexxart n Musa zi jjihet n tes…õa n tqebbaŇô d wezyen n teqbińć. \x ‚óė \xo 14:2 \xt ŇėxŇô. 26:55\x*  
\v 3 Ma…£ar Musa tu…£a iwca i tnayen n tqebbaŇô d wezyen n teqbińć ict n tes…£art a…£irin i L‚ÄôUrdun, \add maca\add* i Ilawiyyen war d asen iwci ca tas…£art di ŇôwesŠĻ≠ nsen.  
\v 4 Aqa ayt n Yusuf ggin tnayen n tqebbaŇô, Manassa d Ifrayim, u i Ilawiyyen war d as wcin ca tas…£art di temmurt maca \add m…£ir\add* tineddam i tzeddi…£t d min i«ßan zzatsent n ddmani n tarewsa i Ňôebhayem u i min …£arsen i«ßan. \f ‚óľ \fr 14:4 \ft \+fk Ilawiyyen\ft  - ixs ad yini ‚Äėayt n Lawi‚Äô.\f*  
\v 5 Am mammec tu…£a yumur SIDI i Musa, ammu i ggin ayt n Israil Ňôami bŠłćan tammurt.   
\m
\v 6 \add Xenni\add* qarrben-dd ayt n Yahuda …£ar Yacuwa di Jiljal. \bd Kalib\bd*, mmis n Yafunni, Aqinizi, inna as: ‚ÄúCek tessned min xafi d xak inna SIDI i Musa, aryaz n AREBBI, di Qadac-Barni…õ. \x ‚óė \xo 14:6 \xt ŇėxŇô. 14:24; A…õwd. 1:36\x*  
\v 7 Necc ggi…£ areb…õin n isegg ∑usa, umi i dd ayi issekk Musa, amsexxar n SIDI, zi Qadac-Barni…õ maŠł•end ad bergage…£ tammurt u necc …õeqbe…£ …£ares, xebbare…£ as am mammec \add t\add* tu…£a deg wuŇô inu.  
\v 8 \add Waxxa amenni\add* aytma, inni i tu…£a akidi ige…õ…õden, ssfessyen uŇô n Ňôgens, \add maca\add* necc tu…£a Ňôebda Šłćeffare…£ SIDI, AREBBI inu. \x ‚óė \xo 14:8 \xt ŇėxŇô. 14:24\x*  
\v 9 Deg wass nni ijju«ß Musa, inna: ‚Äú\add Wayyaw,\add* maŇôa tammurt i di tessarsed aŠłćar nnec, war tŠĶČttiŇôi i cek d iŠł•enjiren nnec d tas…£art i Ňôebda, minzi tu…£a cek Ňôebda tŠłćeffared SIDI, AREBBI inu!‚ÄĚ   
\m
\v 10 Ňėexxu, xzar, SIDI ijja ayi ddare…£, am mammec issiweŇô. Ňėexxu aqa xemsa u-reb…õin n isegg ∑usa zeg wami issiweŇô SIDI …£ar Musa awaŇô-a, umi Israil yuyur di ŇôexŇôa. Uca Ňôexxu, aqa da, am mammec tŠĶČttwaŇôid, …£ari xemsa u-tmanyin n isegg ∑usa.  
\v 11 Necc …õad meŠł•Šłće…£ am mammec \add meŠł•Šłće…£\add* deg wass nni umi i d ayi dd-issekk Musa. Am mammec tu…£a jehhde…£ deg wussan nni, ammu i jehhde…£ …õawed iŠłća i umen…£i maŠł•end ad ff…£e…£ u ad aregg ∑Šł•e…£. \x ‚óė \xo 14:11 \xt ŇėxŇô. 27:17; A…õwd. 31:2\x*  
