\v 1 \bd TaqedduŠł•t\bd* i ayt n \bd Yahuda\bd*, …õlaŠł•sab Ňôa«ßat nsen, tekkar-asent …£ar weymir n Idum, ŇôexŇôa n ŠĻĘin, …£ar ljanub, \add aŇô\add* ljanub qa…õ.  
