\c 16
\s1 Tas…£art n ayt n Yusuf: Manassi d Ifrayim  
\m
\v 1 \bd TaqedduŠł•t\bd* i ayt n \bd Yusuf\bd* tekkar as-dd zi L‚ÄôUrdun …£ar AriŠł•a, \add uca aymir\add* ittekk x tma n ccarq n waman n AriŠł•a, \add x\add* ŇôexŇôa nni dd-ittge…õ…õaden zi AriŠł•a x idurar n Bayt-Il.  
\v 2 U zi Bayt-Il itteffe…£ …£ar Luz, ittekk x temmurt n ayt n Arkit …£ar ∆źaŠĻ≠arut  
\v 3 uca ihekkwa-dd …£ar Ňô…£arb …£ar temmurt n IfalaŠĻ≠iyyen aŇô tammurt n Bayt-Šł§urun n wadday u aŇô Jazar u ŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠rufa nnes ttakkwaŠłćen aŇô ŇôebŠł•ar.   
