\v 7 u zi YanuŠł•a ihekkwa …£ar ∆źaŠĻ≠arut d Na…õarata uca …õŇôayen ineŠł•Šł•ed AriŠł•a u \add xenni\add* itteffe…£ …£ar L‚ÄôUrdun.  
