\c 17
\m
\v 1 Tu…£a din \add …õawed\add* ict n \bd taqedduŠł•t\bd* i teqbińć n \bd Manassa\bd*, minzi netta tu…£a d amenzu n Yusuf, tekkar as-dd i Makir, amenzu n Manassa, babas n \add temmurt n\add* Jil…õad, Jil…õad d Bacan, ma…£ar netta tu…£a d ijj n u…õeskari imeŠł•Šłćen. \x ‚óė \xo 17:1 \xt Amz. 46:20\x*  
\v 2 Tekkar asen-dd tqedduŠł•t i ayt iqqimen n Manassa …õlaŠł•sab Ňôa«ßat nsen, i ayt n Abi…õazar d ayt n Šł§alaq d ayt n Asriyil d ayt n Cakam d ayt n Šł§afar d ayt n Camida…õ. Ina d ayt n Manassa, mmis n Yusuf, …õlaŠł•sab Ňôa«ßat nsen.   
\m
\v 3 U ZeluŠł•fad, mmis n Šł§afar, mmis n Jil…õad, mmis n Makir, mmis n Manassa, war …£ares tu…£i ca iŠł•enjiren, maca tu…£a …£ares yessis. Ina d ismawen n yessis: MaŠł•la d Nu…õa, Šł§ujla, Milka d TirŠĻ£a. \x ‚óė \xo 17:3 \xt ŇėxŇô. 26:33; 27:1\x*  
\v 4 Nitenti qarrbent-i-dd zzat i wudem n ukehhan Ali…õazar u zzat i wudem n Yacuwa, mmis n Nun, u zzat i wudem n ŇôŠł•ukkam, nnant: ‚ÄúSIDI yumur Musa, ad ane…£ iwc tas…£art jar aytmatne…£.‚ÄĚ Uca iwca asent, …õlaŠł•sab Ňôumur n SIDI, ict n tas…£art jar wawmaten n babatsent. \x ‚óė \xo 17:4 \xt ŇėxŇô. 27:7; 36:2\x*   
\m
\v 5 Ammu i iwŠłćan ifiŇôan \add n Ňôe…õbar\add* …õecra n twaŇôawin i Manassa, bŇôa tammurt n Jil…õad d Bacan i i«ßan a…£irin n L‚ÄôUrdun.  
\v 6 Ma…£ar yessis n Manassa ŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠fent tas…£art di ŇôwesŠĻ≠ n warrawen nnes u tammurt n Jil…õad tu…£a i warrawen n Manassa i iqqimen.   
