\v 7 Aymir n Manassa itteffe…£ zi Acir i…õeddu …£ar Mikmata i i«ßan ajemmaŠłć i Cakim u aymir itteffe…£ …£ar ufusi …£ar imezda…£ n ∆źayn-TaffuŠł•.  
\v 8 Manassa …£ares tammurt n TaffuŠł•, maca TaffuŠł• \add simant nnes\add* \add nni\add* i«ßan x weymir ak-d Manassa, tu…£a i ayt n Ifrayim.  
\v 9 \add Xenni\add* ihekkwa weymir …£ar te…£zart n Qana …£ar ljanub n te…£zart. Tineddam n Ifrayim aqa-tent din jar tneddam n Manassa. Tammurt n Manassa te«ßa …£ar tma n ccamal n i…£zar uca ŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠rufa nnes ttakkwaŠłćen aŇô ŇôebŠł•ar.  
\v 10 Ljanub aqa n Ifrayim, ccamal aqa n Manassa u ŇôebŠł•ar d aymir nnes. Di ccamal ttenŠł•adan x Acir u di ccarq x Issakar.  
\v 11 Di Issakar u di Acir dewŇôen ina …£ar Manassa: Bayt-Can ak-d tneddam i …£ares dd-iqqnen u Yabla…õam ak-d tneddam nnes d imezda…£ n Dur ak-d tneddam nnes d imezda…£ n ∆źayn-Dur ak-d tneddam nnes d imezda…£ n Ta…õnak ak-d tneddam nnes d imezda…£ n Majiddu ak-d tneddam nnes, tŇôata n treqqi…õin uyŇôent.  
\v 12 Ayt n Manassa war zemmaren ad \add zzaysen\add* ŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠fen tineddam-a \add d tes…£art n Ňôwart\add*, minzi ayt n Ken…õan ggin \add ad qqimen\add* zedd…£en di temmurt. \x ‚óė \xo 17:12 \xt ŇėqŠłć. 1:27\x*  
\v 13 Umi ayt n Israil dewŇôen jehden, ggin nitni ljizya x ayt n Ken…õan, \add maca\add* war xasen uŠļďŠļďŇôen qa…õ.  
\v 14 SsiwŇôen ayt n Yusuf ak-d Yacuwa, nnan: ‚ÄúMayemmi d ayi tewcid d tas…£art m…£ir ict n tqedduŠł•t d yijj n ufiŇôu \add n Ňôe…õbar\add*, waxxa necc d ijj n Ňôgens d ameqqran, awarni i umi d ayi igga SIDI lbaraka ammu?‚ÄĚ  
\v 15 Yacuwa inna asen: ‚ÄúMaŇôa cek \add xenni\add* d ijj n Ňôgens ameqqran, ge…õ…õed \add xenni\add* …£ar wez…£ar uca zdem dinni ttasi…õ i yixef nnec di temmurt n Ifiriziyyen d Irafawiyyen, maŇôa Šł•ŠĻ£aren xak idurar n Ifrayim.‚ÄĚ \f ‚óľ \fr 17:15 \ft \+fk az…£ar\ft  - ni…£ ‚ÄėŇô…£abet‚Äô ni…£ ‚Äėtazgant‚Äô.\f*  
