\v 18 ma…£ar uŇôa d idurar ad iŇôin nwem uca umi \add te«ßa\add* d az…£ar, ittxeŠĻ£ŠĻ£a ad tzedmem uca ŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠rufa nnes ad iŇôin i kenniw, ma…£ar ad taŠļďŠļďŇôem x ayt n Ken…õan \add zi tes…£art nsen\add*, waxxa …£arsen ikarruten n umen…£i n wuzzaŇô u waxxa nitni jehden.‚ÄĚ   
