\v 5 Ad tt bŠłćan x seb…õa n tseqqar. Yahuda ad iqqim x temmurt nnes di ljanub u taddart n Yusuf ad teqqim x temmurt nnes di ccamal.  
\v 6 Kenniw ad tzemmem tammurt x seb…õa n tseqqar uca izemmanen nni ad ayi ten dd-tawyem danita, \add xenni\add* necc ad awem nŠłćare…£ taqedduŠł•t zzat i wudem n SIDI, AREBBI nne…£.  
\v 7 Minzi Ilawiyyen war …£arsen bu tas…£art di¬†Ňôwest nwem, minzi tukehhant n SIDI d tas…£art nsen. Jad d Rubin d wezyen n teqbińć n Manassa ŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠fen tas…£art nsen x ujemmaŠłć n L‚ÄôUrdun, …£ar ccarq, \add tas…£art\add* nni i d asen iwca Musa, amsexxar n SIDI.   
