\v 2 ‚ÄúSiweŇô ak-d ayt n Israil, ini: ‚ÄėAd tfarzem tineddam n tarewŇôa i yixef nwem, min xef d awem ssiwŇôe…£ s tsexxart n Musa, \f ‚óľ \fr 20:2 \ft \+fk s tsexxart n Musa\ft  - s lŠł•arf: ‚Äės ufus n Musa‚Äô, ixs ad yini ‚Äės uqemmum n Musa‚Äô ni…£ ‚Äės Ňôumur n Musa‚Äô.\f*¬†¬†\x ‚óė \xo 20:2 \xt  Uf. 21:13; ŇėxŇô. 35:6; A…õwd. 19:1, 2\x*  
\v 3 Šł•ima ad yarweŇô din uqettaŇô nni in…£in ijj n bnadem zeg uweddar, bŇôa ma ad as igg ŇôeŠł•sab. Ad iŇôint d imucan mani …£a tarewŇôem zeg uneqqam n idammen. \f ‚óľ \fr 20:3 \ft \+fk bnadem\ft  - s T…õibranit ‚ÄėŇôe…õmar‚Äô.\f*  
\v 4 MaŇôa netta yarweŇô …£ar icten zi tneddam nni, ad ibedd …£ar tewwart n tendint uca ad iŠł•aja tamsart nnes deg imezzu…£en n imeqqranen n tendint. \add Xenni\add* ad t ssidfen di tendint, ad as wcen ijj n wemcan maŠł•end ad …£arsen izde…£. \x ‚óė \xo 20:4 \xt  ŇėxŇô. 35:22, 23; A…õwd. 19:4, 5\x*  
\v 5 MaŇôa \add xenni\add* iŠłćfar i-t uneqqam n idammen, war d as tticen aqettaŇô deg ufus nnes, ma…£ar netta in…£a jjar nnes bŇôa ma ad as igg ŇôeŠł•sab, tu…£a war t icarreh ca iŠłćennaŠłć ni…£ fariŠłćennaŠłć.  
\v 6 Netta ad iqqim izde…£ di tendint nni, aŇô …£a ibedd i ŇôeŠł•kam zzat i wudem n tmesmunt, \add uca awarni man aya\add* aŇô …£a immet arrays n ikehhanen wenni din i«ßan deg wussan nni. Xenni izemmar uqettaŇô ad i…õqeb …£ar tendint nnes u …£ar taddart nnes, …£ar tendint i zi dd-yarweŇô.   
\m
\v 7 \add Xenni\add* qeddsen Qadac deg idurar n Naftali di Ljalil u Cakim x idurar n Ifrayim u Qaryat-Arba…õ, tenni d Šł§abrun, di Temmurt n Idurar n Yahuda.  
\v 8 A…£irin n L‚ÄôUrdun, di jjihet n ccarq zi AriŠł•a, wcin nitni zi teqbińć n Rubin BaŠĻ£ar di ŇôexŇôa x ŇôwaŠĻ≠a \add yu…õŇôan\add* u zi teqbińć n Jad \add wcin nitni\add* Ramut di Jil…õad u zi teqbińć n Manassa \add tandint n\add* Julan di Bacan. \x ‚óė \xo 20:8 \xt A…õwd. 4:43\x*   
\m
\v 9 Tina d tineddam nni ittwaggen i marra ayt n Israil u i ubarrani nni i izedd…£en di ŇôwesŠĻ≠ nsen, Šł•ima kuŇô ijj zeg inni in…£in ijj n bnadem s uweddar, izemmar ad din yarweŇô, Šł•ima war ittmetti s ufus n ineqqamen n idammen aŇô …£a ibedd i¬†ŇôŠł•ukm zzat i wudem n tmesmunt. \f ‚óľ \fr 20:9 \ft \+fk bnadem\ft  - di T…õibranit ‚ÄėŇôe…õmar‚Äô.\f*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 21
\s1 Tineddam n Ilawiyyen  
\m
\v 1 \add Xenni\add* qarrben-dd ize«ßifen n \add tudrin n\add* ibabaten n Ilawiyyen …£ar ukehhan Ali…õazar d Yacuwa, mmis n Nun, u \add qarrben-dd\add* …£ar ize«ßifen n \add tudrin n\add* ibabaten n tqebbaŇô n ayt n Israil. \x ‚óė \xo 21:1 \xt 1 Im. 6:39\x*  
\v 2 SsiwŇôen akidsen di Cilu di temmurt n Ken…õan, nnan: ‚ÄúSIDI yumur s ufus n Musa, ad ane…£ mmewcent tneddam, Šł•ima ad daysent nezde…£, ak-d ddmani nsent n tarewsa i Ňôebhayem nne…£.‚ÄĚ \x ‚óė \xo 21:2 \xt ŇėxŇô. 35\x*  
\v 3 \add Xenni\add* wcin ayt n Israil s Ňôumur n SIDI, zi tes…£art nsen, tineddam ak-d ddmani nsent n tarewsa i Ilawiyyen.   
\b  
\m
\v 4 Uca tekkar asent-dd tqedduŠł•t i Ňôa«ßat n \bd Qahat\bd*. S tqedduŠł•t kkarent asen-dd i warraw n ukehhan Harun zeg Ilawiyyen \bd tŇôeŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠ac n tneddam\bd* zi \add temmurt n\add* teqbińć n Yahuda u n teqbińć n Cim…õun u n teqbińć n Binyamin.  
\v 5 I inni iqqimen n ayt n Qahat \add kkarent asen-dd\add* s tqedduŠł•t …õecra n tneddam zi \add temmurt n\add* Ňôa«ßat n teqbińć n Ifrayim u n teqbińć n Dan u n wezyen n teqbińć n Manassa.   
\m
\v 6 I \bd ayt n Jarcun\bd* \add kkarent asen-dd\add* s tqedduŠł•t \bd tŇôeŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠ac n tneddam\bd* zi \add temmurt n\add* Ňôa«ßat n teqbińć n Issakar u n teqbińć n Acir u n teqbińć n Naftali u n wezyen n teqbińć n Manassa di Bacan.   
\m
\v 7 I \bd ayt n Marari\bd* \add kkarent asen-dd s tqedduŠł•t\add* \bd ten…õac n tneddam\bd*, …õlaŠł•sab Ňôa«ßat nsen, zi \add temmurt n\add* teqbińć n Rubin u n teqbińć n Jad u n teqbińć n Zabulun.  
\v 8 Ayt n Israil wcin tineddam-a ak-d ddmani nsent n tarewsa s tqedduŠł•t i Ilawiyyen, am mammec \add t\add* yumur SIDI s tsexxart n Musa.   
\b  
\m
\v 9 Zi \add temmurt n\add* teqbińć n ayt n Yahuda u zi teqbińć n ayt n Cim…õun wcin asen tineddam-a i ittwannan s yisem nsent  
\v 10 u \add marra aya\add* ikkar asen-dd \bd i warraw n Harun \+bdit nni i«ßan\+bdit* zi Ňôa«ßat n Iqahatiyyen\bd* zeg ayt n Lawi, minzi taqedduŠł•t tamezwarut tewŠłća xasen.  
\v 11 Nitni wcin asen tandint n Arba…õ, babas n ∆źanaq, tenni d Šł§abrun, di Temmurt n Idurar n Yahuda ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa i d as dd-innŠłćen. \f ‚óľ \fr 21:11 \ft \+fk tandint n Arba…õ\ft  - ni…£ ‚ÄėQaryat-Arba…õ‚Äô.\f*  
\v 12 \add Maca\add* iyyaren n tendint d Ňôedcur nnes wcin ten d agŇôa i Kalib, mmis n Yafunni.  
\v 13 I ayt n ukehhan Harun wcin asen \add tineddam-a d\add* tandint n tarewŇôa i uqettaŇô: Šł§abrun ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa, d Libna ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa,  
\v 14 d Yattir ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa, d Ictuma…õ ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa,  
\v 15 d Šł§ulun ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa, d Dabir ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa,  
\v 16 d ∆źayn ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa, d YuŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠a ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa, d Bayt-Cams ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa, \add marra jmi…õ\add* tu…£a atent di \bd tes…õa n tneddam\bd* zi tnayen n tqebbaŇô-a.   
\m
\v 17 Zi teqbińć n Binyamin \add wcin asen\add* Jib…õun ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa, d Jib…õa ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa,  
\v 18 ∆źanatut ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa, d ∆źalmun ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa. \add Marra jmi…õ\add* tu…£a atent di \bd areb…õa n tneddam\bd*.  
\v 19 Marra tineddam n warraw n Harun, n ikehhanen, \add tu…£a atent di\add* \bd tŇôeŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠ac n tneddam\bd* ak-d ddmani nsent n tarewsa.   
\m
\v 20 \bd I Ňôa«ßat n ayt n Qahat, Ilawiyyen, nni iqqimen zeg ayt n Qahat\bd* kkarent asen-dd s tqedduŠł•t tineddam zi \add temmurt n\add* teqbińć n Ifrayim.  
\v 21 Wcin asen \add tineddam-a d\add* tandint n tarewŇôa i uqettaŇô: Cakim ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa x idurar n Ifrayim, d Jazar ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa,  
\v 22 d QibŠĻ£ayim ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa, d Bayt-Šł§urun ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa. \add Marra jmi…õ\add* tu…£a atent di \bd areb…õa n tneddam\bd*.   
\m
\v 23 Zi teqbińć n Dan \add kkarent asen-dd:\add* Iltaqa ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa, Jibbatun ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa,  
\v 24 Ayalun ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa d Jad-Rimmun ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa. \add Marra jmi…õ\add* tu…£a atent di \bd areb…õa n tneddam\bd*.   
\m
\v 25 Zi \add temmurt n\add* wezyen n teqbińć n Manassa \add kkarent asen-dd\add* Ta…õnak ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa d Jad-Rimmun ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa. \add Marra jmi…õ\add* tu…£a atent di \bd tnayen n tneddam\bd*.  
\v 26 Marra tineddam i Ňôa«ßat n ayt n Qahat nni iqqimen \add tu…£a atent\add* di …õecra n tneddam ak-d ddmani nsent n tarewsa.   
\b  
\m
\v 27 Zi \add temmurt n\add* wezyen n teqbińć n Manassa \add kkarent asen-dd tneddam-a\add* \bd i ayt n Jarcun\bd*, zi Ňôa«ßat n Ilawiyyen, am tendint n tarewŇôa i uqettaŇô: Julan di Bacan ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa d Ba…õactara ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa. \add Marra jmi…õ\add* \add tu…£a atent di\add* \bd tnayen n tneddam\bd*.   
\m
\v 28 Zi \add temmurt n\add* teqbińć n Issakar \add kkarent asen-dd:\add* Qicyun ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa, d Dabrat ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa,  
\v 29 Yarmut ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa, d ∆źayn-Jannim ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa. \add Marra jmi…õ\add* \add tu…£a atent di\add* \bd areb…õa n tneddam\bd*.   
\m
\v 30 Zi \add temmurt n\add* teqbińć n Acir \add kkarent asen-dd:\add* Mic-Al ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa, d ∆źabdun ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa,  
\v 31 d Šł§alqat ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa d RaŠł•ub ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa. \add Marra jmi…õ\add* \add tu…£a atent di\add* \bd areb…õa n tneddam\bd*.   
\m
\v 32 Zi \add temmurt n\add* teqbińć n Naftali \add kkarent asen-dd\add* am tendint n tarewŇôa i uqettaŇô: Qadac di Ljalil ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa, d Šł§ammut-Dur ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa d Qartan ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa. \add Marra jmi…õ\add* \add tu…£a atent\add* di \bd tŇôata n tneddam\bd*.  
\v 33 Marra tineddam n ayt n Jarcun …õlaŠł•sab Ňôa«ßat nsen \add tu…£a atent di\add* tŇôeŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠ac n tneddam ak-d ddmani nsent n tarewsa.   
\b  
\m
\v 34 \bd I Ňôa«ßat n ayt n Marari\bd*, aqa aten d inni iqqimen \add …õad\add* zeg Ilawiyyen, \add mmewcent asen\add* zi \add temmurt n\add* teqbińć n Zabulun, Juqna…õam ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa, Qarta ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa,  
\v 35 Dimna ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa d Nahalal ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa. \add Marra jmi…õ\add* tu…£a atent di \bd areb…õa n tneddam\bd*.   
\m
\v 36 Zi \add temmurt n\add* teqbińć n Rubin \add kkarent asen-dd\add* BaŠĻ£ar ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa, d YahŠĻ£a ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa,  
\v 37 Qadimut ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa d Mafa…õa ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa. \add Marra jmi…õ\add* \add tu…£a atent di\add* \bd areb…õa n tneddam\bd*.   
\m
\v 38 Zi \add temmurt n\add* teqbińć n Jad \add kkarent asen-dd\add* am tendint n tarewŇôa i uqettaŇô: Ramut di Jil…õad ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa, d MaŠł•anayim ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa,  
\v 39 Šł§acbun ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa, d Ya…õzir ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa. \add Marra jmi…õ\add* \add tu…£a atent di\add* \bd areb…õa n tneddam\bd*.   
\m
\v 40 \add Tu…£a tina\add* marra d tineddam i ayt n Marari, …õlaŠł•sab Ňôa«ßat nsen, tinni iqqimen zi Ňôa«ßat n Ilawiyyen, tinni x dd-tewŠłća tqedduŠł•t nsen, \bdit marra jmi…õ tu…£a tent di\bdit* \bd ten…õac n tneddam\bd*.   
\b  
\m
\v 41 \bd Marra tineddam\bd* di ŇôwesŠĻ≠ n Ňôwart n ayt n Israil \add tu…£a atent di\add* \bd tmenya u-reb…õin n tneddam\bd* ak-d ddmani nsent n tarewsa.  
\v 42 Tineddam-a tu…£a atent marra ak-d ddmani nsent n tarewsa i d asent innŠłćen. Ammu \add i tu…£a te«ßa\add* …£ar marra tineddam-a.   
\m
\v 43 Ammu iwca SIDI i Israil marra tammurt nni tu…£a ijju«ß ad tt iwc i Ňôejdud nsen uca nitni warten tt uca ruŠł•en zedd…£en dayes.  
\v 44 Uca SIDI igga asen Ňôhudnet zi marra i…£ezdisen, am mammec marra nni tu…£a ijju«ß i Ňôejdud nsen. UŇôa d ijj zi¬†Ňô…õedyan nsen war d asen izemmar zzat i wudem nsen. SIDI iwca asen marra Ňô…õedyan deg ufus nsen.  
\v 45 UŇôa d ijj n wawaŇô zi marra awaŇôen icnan i zi issiweŇô SIDI …£ar taddart n Israil iwŠłća. Marra \add aya\add* ittwakemmeŇô.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 22
\s1 A…õqab n tqebbaŇô i i«ßan …£ar ujemmaŠłć n L‚ÄôUrdun  
\m
\v 1 Xenni iŇôa…£a-dd Yacuwa i Irubiniyyen d Ijadiyyen d wezyen n teqbińć n Manassa,  
\v 2 inna asen: ‚ÄúKenniw teŠł•Šłćam marra min xef i d awem yumur Musa, amsexxar n SIDI, u kenniw tesŇôam \add …õawed\add* i tmijja inu di marra min xef d awem umure…£. \x ‚óė \xo 22:2 \xt ŇėxŇô. 32:20; A…õwd. 3:18\x*  
\v 3 Kenniw war tesmiŠł•em ca deg aytmatwem deg waŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠as n wussan aŇô ass-a u teŠł•Šłćam aŠł•eŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠u n Ňôumur n SIDI, AREBBI nwem.  
\v 4 Uca Ňôexxu igga SIDI, AREBBI nwem, i aytmatwem arraŠł•et, am mammec tu…£a i d asen tt iwa…õd. ∆źeqbem xenni Ňôexxu …£ar iqiŠłćan nwem di temmurt n Ňôwart nwem nni d awem iwca Musa, amsexxar n SIDI, x ujemmaŠłć n L‚ÄôUrdun. \x ‚óė \xo 22:4 \xt ŇėxŇô. 32:33; A…õwd. 3:13; 29:8; Yac. 13:8\x*  
\v 5 Maca Šł•Šłćam mliŠł• ad teggem Ňôumur d Ccari…õa i d awem iwca Musa, amsexxar n SIDI, Šł•ima ad texsem SIDI, AREBBI nwem, ad tuyurem di marra ibriden nnes, ad teŠł•Šłćam marra Ňôumurat nnes uca ad …£ares tŇôeŠĻ£qem u ad as tsexxarem s marra wuŇô d marra Ňôe…õmar nwem.‚ÄĚ \x ‚óė \xo 22:5 \xt A…õwd. 10:12\x*   
\m
\v 6 Ibarek i-ten Yacuwa, ijja i-ten ad uyuren uca nitni aregg ∑Šł•en …£ar iqiŠłćan nsen.  
\v 7 I wezyen n teqbińć n Manassa tu…£a iwca Musa ict n tes…£art di Bacan, maca i yijj n wezyen nne…£ni iwca as Yacuwa ict n tes…£art …£ar aytmatsen x u…£ezdis-a n L‚ÄôUrdun zi manis t…£e«ßi tfuct. Umi ten issekk Yacuwa …£ar iqiŠłćan nsen, ibarek i-ten  
\v 8 uca issiweŇô akidsen, inna: ‚ÄúS wagŇôa d ameqqran ad t…õeqbem …£ar iqiŠłćan nwem, s waŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠as n Ňôebhayem u s nnuqart d wure…£ u s nnŠł•as d wuzzaŇô u s waŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠as n warruŠłć. BŠłćam takeccaŠłćt n Ňô…õedyan nwem ak-d aytmatwem.‚ÄĚ  
\v 9 ∆źeqben ayt n Rubin d ayt n Jad d wezyen n teqbińć n Manassa, ff…£en zi …£ar ayt n Israil, igg ∑ejjen x Cilu \add nni i«ßan\add* di temmurt n Ken…õan, Šł•ima ad raŠł•en …£ar temmurt n Jil…õad, …£ar temmurt n ŇômuŇôk nsen nni iŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠fen d agŇôa …õlaŠł•sab Ňôumur n SIDI s tsexxart n Musa.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 A…õaltar n tqebbaŇô …£ar ujemmaŠłć n L‚ÄôUrdun  
\m
\v 10 \add Umi\add* iwŠłćen nitni …£ar tmuwwa n L‚ÄôUrdun nni \add i«ßan …õad\add* di temmurt n Ken…õan, bnan ayt n Rubin d ayt n Jad d wezyen n teqbińć n Manassa dinni ijj n u…õalŠĻ≠ar …£ar L‚ÄôUrdun, ijj n u…õalŠĻ≠ar im…£ar aŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠as. \x ‚óė \xo 22:10 \xt Yac. 18:7\x*  
\v 11 Uca sŇôin ayt n Israil aqa qqaren: ‚ÄúXzarem, ayt n Rubin d ayt n Jad d wezyen n teqbińć n Manassa bnan ijj n u…õalŠĻ≠ar …£ar weymir n temmurt n Ken…õan x tmuwwa n L‚ÄôUrdun, x u…£ezdis \add n L‚ÄôUrdun\add* n ayt n Israil.‚ÄĚ  
\v 12 \add Umi\add* sŇôin ayt n Israil aya, tmun marra tmesmunt n ayt n Israil di Cilu Šł•ima ad ff…£en i umen…£i akidsen s ijj n Ňô…õeskar.  
\v 13 Uca ssekken ayt n Israil FinaŠł•as, mmis n ukehhan Ali…õazar, …£ar ayt n Rubin u …£ar ayt n Jad u …£ar wezyen n teqbińć n Manassa di Jil…õad,  
\v 14 u \add ssekken\add* akides …õecra n ŇôŠł•ukkam, ijj n ŇôŠł•akem zi kuŇô taddart n babas, zi marra tiqebbaŇô n Israil. KuŇô ijj \add zzaysen\add* tu…£a d aze«ßif n taddart n Ňôejdud nsen i ŇôuŇôuf n Israil.   
\m
\v 15 Usin-dd nitni …£ar ayt n Rubin u …£ar ayt n Jad u …£ar wezyen n teqbińć n Manassa di temmurt n Jil…õad, nnan asen:  
\v 16 ‚ÄúAmmu i tessiweŇô marra tmesmunt n SIDI: Min ixs ad yini Ňôe…£dar-a i zi te…£darem AREBBI n Israil umi tŠł•eyydem ass-a zi¬†Šłćeffar n SIDI, umi tebnam i yixef nwem ijj n u…õalŠĻ≠ar maŠł•end ad t…£eww…£em x SIDI ass-a?  
\v 17 Ma war i«ßi cfa ane…£ Ňômu…õŠĻ£iyyet n Fa…£ur, \add Ňômu…õŠĻ£iyyet i zi\add* …£ar ass-a \add …õad\add* war nettwassizdeg u zzayes i tewŠłća jjriŠł•ect x tmesmunt n SIDI?\x ‚óė \xo 22:17 \xt ŇėxŇô. 25:3; A…õwd. 4:3\x*  
\v 18 Ma aqa kenniw ass-a tewcim s we…õrur i SIDI uca ad imsar \add xenni\add*, umi …£a t…£eww…£em ass-a x SIDI, ad iffugem Netta x marra tmesmunt n Israil?  
\v 19 MaŇôa ze…õma texmej temmurt i i«ßan d agŇôa nwem, \add xenni\add* …õdum …£ar temmurt nni i«ßan d agŇôa n SIDI u mani te«ßa Tzeddi…£t n SIDI uca ksim i yixef nwem ijj n wegra di ŇôwesŠĻ≠ nne…£, \add maca\add* war t…£eww…£em ca x SIDI u war t…£eww…£em ca xane…£ umi …£a tebnam ijj n u…õalŠĻ≠ar i yixef nwem, m…£ir a…õalŠĻ≠ar n SIDI, AREBBI nne…£.  
\v 20 Ma tu…£a ∆źaxan, mmis n ZaraŠł•, war i…£dar di tmesŇôact n min ittwaŠł•arrmen \add i uteŠł•Šł•i\add* u xenni ma war dd-ittis uduqqez n we…£Šłćab x marra tamesmunt n Israil? Uca aryaz nni war immut weŠł•Šł•Šłćes waha di Ňômu…õŠĻ£iyyet nnes.‚Äô‚ÄĚ   
\m
\v 21 \add Xenni\add* arrin-dd ayt n Rubin d ayt n Jad d wezyen n teqbińć n Manassa uca ssiwŇôen ak-d ize«ßifen x ŇôuŇôuf n Israil:  
\v 22 ‚ÄúArebbi x \add marra\add* irebbiten, SIDI, Arebbi x \add marra\add* irebbiten issen \add i-t\add* u Israil ad \add t\add* issen \add …õawed\add*! MaŇôa iffe…£-dd aya zeg u…£ewwe…£ ni…£ zi Ňôe…£dar x SIDI, \add xenni\add* war xane…£ tceŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠ar ca ass-a, \x ‚óė \xo 22:22 \xt Izhd. 50:1\x*  
\v 23 \add maŇôa tu…£a\add* Šł•ima ad nebna i neccin ijj n u…õalŠĻ≠ar maŠł•end ad newc s we…õrur i SIDI ni…£ \add maŇôa tu…£a\add* Šł•ima ad nqeddem ict n t…£arŠĻ£t n wecmaŠłć ni…£ ict n tewhibt \add n Ňô…£i«ßet\add* ni…£ i usewjed n t…£arŠĻ£a n Ňôehna, ejj SIDI simant nnes ad \add t\add* ibeqqec.  
\v 24 \add Uct xane…£\add*, maŇôa war neggi aya zeg wemnus umi neqqar: ‚ÄėIŠł•enjiren nwem \add zemmaren\add* ad inin i iŠł•enjiren nne…£ tiwecca: Min jar awem-dd ak-d SIDI, AREBBI n Israil?  
\v 25 SIDI igga L‚ÄôUrdun d aymir jar ane…£ d kenniw, ayt n Rubin d ayt n Jad! Kenniw war …£arwem ca tas…£art di SIDI!‚Äô \add Ammu\add* zemmaren ad ssbedden iŠł•enjiren nwem iŠł•enjiren nne…£ x tigg ∑udi n SIDI.  
\v 26 \add X uyenni\add* nenna: Ejj ane…£ ad nebna a…õalŠĻ≠ar-a, war i«ßi i t…£arŠĻ£t n wecmaŠłć uŇôa i t…£arŠĻ£t,  
\v 27 \add maca\add* Šł•ima ad yiŇôi d acehhad jar neccin d kenniw u jar jjiŇôat nne…£ awarni ane…£, Šł•ima ad nsexxar di tsexxart n SIDI zzat i wudem nnes s t…£arŠĻ£i nne…£ n wecmaŠłć d t…£arŠĻ£i nne…£ \add nne…£ni\add* d t…£arŠĻ£i nne…£ n Ňôehna u Šł•ima iŠł•enjiren nwem war qqaren i iŠł•enjiren nne…£: Kenniw war …£arwem ca tas…£art di SIDI. \x ‚óė \xo 22:27 \xt Amz. 31:48; Yac. 24:27\x*  
\v 28 Neccin nenna: MaŇôa imsar tiwecca ad inin nitni aya i neccin u i jjiŇôat \add awarni ane…£\add*, xenni ad nini: ‚ÄėXzarem, amedya n Ňôebni n u…õalŠĻ≠ar-a n SIDI nni iggin Ňôejdud nne…£, war i«ßi i t…£arŠĻ£t n wecmaŠłć ni…£ i t…£arŠĻ£t \add nne…£ni\add*, \add maca\add* Šł•ima ad yiŇôi d acehhad jar neccin d kenniw.‚Äô  
\v 29 Igg ∑ej xane…£ aqa neccin ad n…£ewwe…£ x SIDI ni…£ ass-a ad newc s we…õrur i SIDI umi …£a nebna ijj n u…õalŠĻ≠ar i t…£arŠĻ£t n wecmaŠłć ni…£ i tewhibt \add n Ňô…£i«ßet\add* ni…£ i t…£arŠĻ£t \add nne…£ni\add*, illa a…õalŠĻ≠ar n SIDI, AREBBI nne…£, wenni i«ßan zzat i Tzeddi…£t nnes.‚ÄĚ   
\m
\v 30 Akehhan FinaŠł•as d ŇôŠł•ukkam n tmesmunt d ize«ßifen x ŇôuŇôuf n Israil nni kides \add i«ßan\add*, sŇôin awaŇôen i issiwŇôen ayt n Rubin d ayt n Jad d ayt n Manassa u tu…£a aya d lemliŠł• di tiŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠awin nsen.  
\v 31 FinaŠł•as, mmis n Ali…õazar, inna i ayt n Rubin u i ayt n Jad u i ayt n Manassa: ‚ÄúAss-a ad tessnem belli SIDI aqa-t di ŇôwesŠĻ≠ nne…£ umi kenniw war te…£darem ca SIDI. S uya kenniw tfekkem ayt n Israil zeg ufus n SIDI.‚ÄĚ   
\m
\v 32 \add Xenni\add* yaregg ∑eŠł• ukehhan FinaŠł•as, mmis n Ali…õazar, ak-d ŇôŠł•ukkam zeg ayt n Rubin d ayt n Jad, zi temmurt n Jil…õad …£ar temmurt n Ken…õan, …£ar ayt n Israil, uca nitni ggin daysen Ňôexbar.  
\v 33 Tu…£a tamesŇôact d lemliŠł• di tiŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠awin n ayt n Israil uca Šł•emden ayt n Israil AREBBI u war d asen nnan …õad ad ff…£en ad mmen…£en maŠł•end ad aredd«ßen tammurt i di tu…£a zedd…£en ayt n Rubin d ayt n Jad.  
\v 34 Ayt n Rubin d ayt n Jad Ňôa…£an as i u…õalŠĻ≠ar nni: ‚ÄúAd yiŇôi d acehhad jar ane…£ aqa SIDI d AREBBI.‚ÄĚ   
