\m  
\c 23
\s1 AwaŇô n Yacuwa i ize«ßifen n Israil  
\m
\v 1 Imsar umi …õdun aŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠as n wussan awarni umi SIDI tu…£a igga i Israil Ňôhudnet zi marra Ňô…õedyan nnes i d as dd-innŠłćen u umi tu…£a Yacuwa iwsar, im…£ar deg wussan,  
\v 2 aqa iŇôa…£a Yacuwa i marra Israil, im…£aren nnes d ize«ßifen nnes d ŇôquŠłćat nnes d imeŠł•Šłćayen nnes, inna asen: ‚ÄúNecc wsare…£ u m…£are…£ deg wussan  
\v 3 uca kenniw teŠļďrim marra min igga SIDI, AREBBI nwem, ak-d marra Ňôegnus-a zzat i tiŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠awin nwem, ma…£ar SIDI, AREBBI nwem Simant nnes, d wenni tu…£a immen…£en di ŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠we…õ nwem.  
\v 4 Xzar necc bŠłći…£ awem Ňôegnus-a i iqqimen jar awem s tqedduŠł•t, am tes…£art \add n Ňôwart\add* i tqebbaŇô nwem, ak-d marra Ňôegnus i teŠł•Šł•i…£ zi L‚ÄôUrdun aŇô ŇôebŠł•ar ameqqran mani t…£e«ßi tfuct.  
\v 5 SIDI, AREBBI nwem, ad xasen ibarrez zzat i wudem nwem u ad xasen yaŠļďŠļďeŇô zzat i wudem nwem zi Ňôwart nsen u kenniw ad tŠĶČŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠fem tammurt nsen d Ňôwart, am mammec i d awem issiweŇô SIDI, AREBBI nwem. \x ‚óė \xo 23:5 \xt Uf. 14:14; 23:27; ŇėxŇô. 33:53; A…õwd. 6:19; Yac. 13:6\x*  
\v 6 Šł§Šłćam aŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠as s jjehd u ggem marra min yurin deg wedlis-a ittwannŠłćen n Ccari…õa n Musa, Šł•ima war xas tŠł•eyyidem uŇôa \add …£ar\add* yefus uŇôa \add …£ar\add* uzeŇômaŠłć, \x ‚óė \xo 23:6 \xt A…õwd. 5:32; 28:14\x*  
\v 7 Šł•ima kenniw war ttŠĻ£uram ixef nwem ak-d Ňôegnus-a inni \add …õad\add* iqqimen …£arwem, u war ttfekkarem \add …õad\add* deg yisem n irebbiten nsen u war \add xasen\add* ttja«ßam u \add Šł•ima\add* kenniw war d asen t…õebbdem u war d asen tŠĶČttbendqem. \x ‚óė \xo 23:7 \xt Uf. 23:13; Izhd. 16:4; Irm. 5:7; ŠĻĘaf. 1:5; Afa. 5:3\x*  
\v 8 Ma…£ar ittxeŠĻ£ŠĻ£a ad tŇôeŠĻ£qem i SIDI, AREBBI nwem, am mammec i t teggim aŇô ass-a. \x ‚óė \xo 23:8 \xt A…õwd. 11:22\x*  
\v 9 SIDI yuŠļďŠļďeŇô x Ňôegnus m…£aren u jjehden zzat i wudem nwem. U xawem kenniw, aŇô ass-a war din Šł•ed i izemmaren ad ibedd zzat i wudem nwem.  
\v 10 Ijj n weryaz zzaywem izemmar ad yaŠļďŠļďeŇô x waŇôef \add n yeryazen\add*, minzi SIDI, AREBBI nwem Simant nnes, d wenni ittmen…£an di ŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠we…õ nwem, am mammec tu…£a akidwem issiweŇô. \x ‚óė \xo 23:10 \xt Lawi 26:8; A…õwd. 32:30\x*  
\v 11 Šł§Šłćam \add xenni\add* aŇô ŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠arf x Ňôe…õmur nwem Šł•ima ad texsem SIDI, AREBBI nwem.  
\v 12 Minzi maŇôa kenniw tŠł•eyydem xas uŇôa d ict n jjurret \add waha\add*, uca ad tŇôeŠĻ£qem i min kidwem iqqimen \add …õad\add* n Ňôegnus, i yinni kiwem iqqimen, uca ad tdewŇôem d iŠłćegg ∑aŇôen u ad …£arsen tadfem u nitni¬†am nne…£ni,  
\v 13 xenni ad tessnem nican, aqa SIDI, AREBBI nwem, war ittiŠļďŠļďeŇô …õad x Ňôegnus-a zzat i wudem nwem. Nitni ad dewŇôen d Ňôfex d tracca i kenniw, d \add tiyyita s\add* urekkuŠłć x i…£ezdisen nwem d isennanen i tiŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠awin nwem, aŇô …£a tŠĶČttwateŠł•Šł•am zi temmurt taŠĻ£ebŠł•ant i d awem iwca SIDI, AREBBI nwem.  
\v 14 Xzar, ass-a necc simant inu ad uyure…£ abrid n marra tammurt u kenniw ad tessnem s marra uŇô nwem u s marra Ňôe…õmar nwem, aqa uŇôa d ijj n wawaŇô zi marra awaŇôen i xawem inna SIDI, AREBBI nwem, war dd-iffi…£. Marra ff…£en-dd xawem, uŇôa d ijj n wawaŇô war iqqim war dd-iffi…£.  
\v 15 Uca ad imsar, am mammec xawem dd-yusa marra awaŇô icnan i kidwem issiweŇô SIDI, AREBBI nwem, ammu i xawem i …£a isseqfeŇô SIDI uŇôa d kuŇô awaŇô i…õeffnen aŇô Netta kenniw iteŠł•Šł•a zi temmurt-a taŠĻ£ebŠł•ant i d awem iwca SIDI, AREBBI nwem.  
\v 16 MaŇôa kenniw t…õeddam x Ňė…õahd n SIDI, AREBBI nwem, \add Ňė…õahd\add* nni x d awem yumur Netta uca kenniw ad tuyurem ad t…õebdem i irebbiten nne…£ni uca ad asen tuŠłćarem, \add xenni\add* ad xawem yare…£ we…£Šłćab n SIDI uca kenniw ad tŠĶČttwateŠł•Šł•am de…£ya zi temmurt taŠĻ£ebŠł•ant i d awem iwca Netta.   
\b  
\b  
