\c 24
\s1 Tajdid n Ňė…õahd n Israil ak-d SIDI  
\m
\v 1 Yacuwa issmun marra tiqebbaŇô n Israil di Cakim uca iŇôa…£a i im…£aren n Israil d ize«ßifen nsen d ŇôquŠłćat nsen d imeŠł•Šłćayen nsen uca nitni ssbedden ixef nsen zzat i wudem n AREBBI.  
\v 2 \add Xenni\add* inna Yacuwa i marra Ňôgens: ‚ÄúAmmu i iqqar SIDI, AREBBI n Israil: ‚ÄėŇėejdud nwem zedd…£en zi cŠł•aŇô uya x ujemmaŠłć n ye…£Šļďar \add n LfuraŠĻ≠\add*, TaraŠł•, babas n Ibrahim d babas n NaŠł•ur, u nitni tu…£a ttsexxaren i irebbiten nne…£ni. \x ‚óė \xo 24:2 \xt Amz. 11:26, 31; A…õwd. 26:5\x*  
\v 3 \add Xenni\add* iwye…£-dd jedditwem Ibrahim zeg u…£irin i i…£zar \add n LfuraŠĻ≠\add* u jji…£ t yuyur di marra tammurt n Ken…õan. Necc arni…£ i zzari…õet nnes u wci…£ as IsŠł•aq. \x ‚óė \xo 24:3 \xt Amz. 12:1, 21:2\x*  
\v 4 I IsŠł•aq wci…£ Ya…õqub d ∆źisu, u i ∆źisu wci…£ \add tammurt n\add* idurar n Sa…õir d tas…£art, \add maca\add* Ya…õqub d iŠł•enjiren nnes hwan …£ar MiŠĻ£ra. \x ‚óė \xo 24:4 \xt Amz. 25:24, 36:8, 46:1\x*  
\v 5 \add Xenni\add* ssekke…£ Musa d Harun uca wti…£ MiŠĻ£ra am mammec \add t\add* ggi…£ di ŇôwesŠĻ≠ nnes u awarni as ssuff…£e…£-dd kenniw. \x ‚óė \xo 24:5 \xt Uf. 3:10-4:17; 12:37\x*  
\v 6 Necc ssuff…£e…£-dd Ňôejdud nwem zi MiŠĻ£ra u kenniw tiwŠłćem-dd …£ar ŇôebŠł•ar u ImiŠĻ£riyyen Šłćfaren ibabaten nwem s ikarruten d imnayen aŇô ŇėebŠł•ar n Telga. \x ‚óė \xo 24:6 \xt Uf. 14:1\x*  
\v 7 Uca s…£uyen …£ar SIDI u Netta igga ta«ßest jar awem d ImiŠĻ£riyyen uca ijja ŇôebŠł•ar issfeyyeŠłć xasen aŇôami ten idŇôa. S tiŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠awin nwem teŠļďrim min ggi…£ di MiŠĻ£ra. \add Awarni aya\add* tu…£a tzedd…£em aŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠as n wussan di ŇôexŇôa.  
\v 8 Necc iwye…£-dd kenniw …£ar temmurt n Imuriyyen i tu…£a izedd…£en a…£irin i L‚ÄôUrdun. Nitni mmen…£en akidwem, \add maca\add* Necc ggi…£ ten deg ufus nwem u kenniw tŠĶČŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠fem tammurt nsen u Necc qŠłći…£ xasen zzat i wudem nwem. \x ‚óė \xo 24:8 \xt ŇėxŇô. 21:21, 33\x*  
\v 9 \add Xenni\add* ikkar Balak, mmis n Saffur, aje«ßid n Mu‚Äôab, uca immne…£ ak-d Israil. Netta issekk Šł•ima ad Ňôa…£an i Bil…õam, mmis n Ba…õur, maŠł•end ad kenniw in…õeŇô.  
\v 10 \add Maca\add* Necc war xse…£ ad sŇôe…£ i Bal…õam. \add S uya\add* ibarek netta i kenniw aŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠as u Necc fekke…£-dd kenniw zeg ufus nnes.  
\v 11 \add Xenni\add* teŠļďwam L‚ÄôUrdun, tusim-dd …£ar AriŠł•a. Imezda…£ n AriŠł•a, mmen…£en akidwem, Imuriyyen d Ifiriziyyen d ayt n Ken…õan d IŠł•ittiyyen d Ijirjasiyyen d IŠł•iwiyyen d Iyabusiyyen uca wci…£ awem ten deg ufus nwem. \x ‚óė \xo 24:11 \xt Yac. 3:14; 6:1, 20; 10:8; 11:8\x*  
\v 12 Necc ssekke…£ irezzan iŠłćar…£aŇôen uca uŠļďŠļďŇôen xasen zzatwem, \add am mammec ttwaŠļďŠļďŇôen\add* tnayen n ije«ßiden nni zzat i wudem nwem. \add D man aya\add* war i«ßi s ssif nwem uŇôa s Ňôqews nwem. \x ‚óė \xo 24:12 \xt Uf. 23:28; A…õwd. 7:20; Izhd. 44:4\x*  
\v 13 Necc wci…£ awem tammurt i x war tarebrem u tineddam nni war tebnim, Šł•ima ad tzedd…£em daysent. Uca teccim \add …õawed\add* zi tzayarin d izemmuren i tu…£a war teŠļďŠļďum.‚Äô\x ‚óė \xo 24:13 \xt A…õwd. 6:10, 11, 12\x*  
\v 14 \add Xenni\add* Ňôexxu, gg ∑edem SIDI uca sexxarem as s Ňôekmaret d Ňôaman. NŠłćarem irebbiten nni umi sexxaren Ňôejdud nwem a…£irin i i…£zar \add n LfuraŠĻ≠\add* u di MiŠĻ£ra uca sexxarem i SIDI.  
\v 15 \add Maca\add* maŇôa war dd-tusi x tiŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠awin nwem maŠł•end ad tsexxarem i SIDI, xenni ixŠłćarem ass-a i man wen umi i …£a tsexxarem, i irebbiten nni umi sexxaren Ňôejdud nwem a…£irin i i…£zar \add n LfuraŠĻ≠\add*, ni…£ i irebbiten n Imuriyyen nni di temmurt nsen tzedd…£em. Necc maca d taddart inu, neccin ad nsexxar i SIDI!‚ÄĚ  
\v 16 \add Xenni\add* yarra-dd Ňôgens: ‚ÄúMan aya igg ∑ej ane…£, aqa neccin ad nejj SIDI ad nexdem irebbiten nne…£ni.  
\v 17 Ma…£ar SIDI d AREBBI nne…£ d Netta i d ane…£-dd issge…õ…õden zi temmurt n MiŠĻ£ra, neccin d Ňôejdud nne…£, zi taddart n tesmu…£i u Netta d wenni iggin Ňôe…õŇôamat timeqqranin zzat i tiŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠awin nne…£ u Netta issŇôeqqa xane…£ di marra abrid i nuyur u jar marra Ňôegnus i umi ncuq \add tammurt nsen\add*.  
\v 18 SIDI yuŠļďŠļďeŇô x marra Ňôegnus zzat i wudem nne…£, uŇôa x Imuriyyen, imezda…£ n temmurt. UŇôa d neccin ad nsexxar i SIDI, ma…£ar Netta d AREBBI nne…£.‚ÄĚ  
\v 19 \add Xenni\add* inna Yacuwa i Ňôgens: ‚ÄúKenniw war tzemmarem ad tsexxarem i SIDI, ma…£ar Netta d AREBBI Amqeddes aŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠as u Netta d ijj n Arebbi ittasmen. Netta war d awem i…£effar ixeŠĻ≠ŠĻ≠an nwem d ddnub nwem.  
\v 20 MaŇôa kenniw tejjim SIDI, ad tsexxarem i irebbiten nne…£ni, \add xenni\add* Netta ad xawem inneqŇôeb, ad d awem igg Ňô…£ar uca ad kenniw iqŠłća, awarni Ňôami Netta igga akidwem \add qbeŇô\add* taŠĻ£ebŠł•ant.‚ÄĚ \x ‚óė \xo 24:20 \xt Yac. 23:15\x*  
\v 21 \add Xenni\add* inna Ňôgens i Yacuwa: ‚ÄúLla, minzi neccin ad nsexxar i SIDI.‚ÄĚ  
\v 22 Inna Yacuwa i Ňôgens: ‚ÄúKenniw d Ňôechud x ixef nwem, aqa kenniw tfarzem SIDI, Šł•ima ad as tsexxarem.‚ÄĚ Nitni nnan ‚Äú\add Neccin\add* d Ňôechud!‚ÄĚ  
\v 23 ‚Äú\add Xenni\add* Ňôexxu, nŠłćarem irebbiten i…£riben nni \add i«ßan\add* di ŇôwesŠĻ≠ nwem u tarrem uŇôawen nwem …£ar SIDI, AREBBI n Israil!‚ÄĚ  
\v 24 Inna Ňôgens i Yacuwa: ‚ÄúNeccin ad nsexxar i SIDI, AREBBI nne…£, uca ad nseŇô i tmijja nnes.‚ÄĚ  
\v 25 Deg wass nni igga Yacuwa ijj n Ňô…õahd ak-d Ňôgens uca igga asen di Cakim tawŠĻ£eyyet d lfariŠłća. \x ‚óė \xo 24:25 \xt Uf. 15:25\x*  
\v 26 Yura Yacuwa awaŇôen-a deg wedlis ittwannŠłćen n Ccari…õa n SIDI uca netta iksi ijj n weŠļďru d ameqqran uca issbedd i-t di Cakim sadu ict n tcejjart n yigg nni ibedden …£ar Zzawect Iqeddsen n SIDI.  
\v 27 Inna Yacuwa i marra Ňôgens: ‚ÄúXzarem, aŠļďru-ya ad xane…£ yiŇôi d acehhad, minzi netta isŇôa marra awaŇôen n SIDI nni kidne…£ issiweŇô u netta ad yiŇôi d acehhad i kenniw Šł•ima war tt…£eccam AREBBI nwem.‚ÄĚ  
\v 28 \add Xenni\add* yarxu Yacuwa i Ňôgens, kuŇô aryaz \add iruŠł•\add* …£ar tes…£art nnes.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Ňėmewt n Yacuwa d Ali…õazir  
\m
\v 29 Awarni i tmesŇôayin-a imsar, belli Yacuwa, mmis n Nun, amsexxar n SIDI, immut, netta d ijj n mmis \add n bnadem\add* …£ares mya u-…õecra n isegg ∑usa.  
